Commentary: WIDE! Shami starts off with a wayward delivery. This is bowled slightly back of a length, way outside the off stump and it shapes further away beyond the pitch line. The umpire indicates that it is wide.
On a length outside off, Travis Head decides to leave this for the keeper to collect.
On a length shaping towards the batter, drifting down leg, Travis Head deflects this off his pads for a single. Leg byes signaled.

FOUR BYES! This ball is moving like a pendulum right now. On a length outside off, Khwaja leaves this and the shape away on this takes it in between the first and second slip for a boundary. Byes signaled.
Fuller one outside off, Usman Khawaja leaves this for the keeper.
FOUR! Edged and gone for four through the slips cordon. Touch fuller around off, Usman Khawaja edges this with soft hands and it flies away for a boundary towards third man through slips.
Fuller delivery around off, Usman Khawaja pushes this to mid off for no run to end an eventful first over with 10 runs coming off it.
Umesh Yadav begins with a good-length delivery but delivers this outside leg, Head leaves this on alone.
Fuller around off, Travis Head guides this to point.
Fuller and on off, Travis Head blocks this out with a front foot defensive stroke.
On a length outside off, Travis Head defends this out.
Fuller and outside off, Travis Head looks to cut but the low bounce beats him and the keeper collects this.
On a length just wide of pads, Travis Head looks to flick but fails to connect. Umesh Yadav begins with a maiden over.
Better start to this over. On a length outside off, Usman Khawaja lets this go.
Fuller one outside off, teasing Usman to drive but he stays calm and leaves this one.
Length dragged back a bit just outside off, Usman Khawaja pushes this to cover point for nothing.
The length is right but the line is a bit too wide as he darts one outside off, Khawaja leaves this with ease.
Fuller one towards his pads, Usman Khawaja flicks this to fine leg for a single.

FOUR BYES! More runs in that extras column. Fuller one swinging in towards the batter, Head looks to drive but gets beaten by the low bounce and late swing on this. The ball bounces awkwardly in front of Srikar Bharat and races away to a boundary for four more byes.
Fuller one outside off, Usman Khawaja lets this go for the keeper to collect.
On a length and on off, Usman Khawaja defends this back to the bowler.
Back of a length but outside off, Usman Khawaja decides not to poke at this.
On a length and on off, Usman Khawaja blocks this out.
Fuller one in middle, Usman Khawaja defends this solidly.
Fuller around off, Usman Khawaja pushes this to short mid wicket for no run. Yet another maiden over bowled by Umesh Yadav.
On a length outside off, Travis Head looks to cut but gets beaten and Srikar Bharat collects this well diving to his left.
On a length around middle, Travis Head pushes this to short mid wicket for no run.
Fuller one around off, Travis Head pushes this to short cover. Rohit does well to deflect this with a diving effort to mid off. Single taken.
On a length around off, Usman Khawaja defends this off the front foot.
On a length just outside off, Usman Khawaja strides out and blocks this towards short cover. Mohammad Shami has overstepped here.
Fuller outside off, Usman Khawaja shuffles and leaves this.
Fuller around middle, Usman Khawaja blocks this out.
Fuller outside off, Travis Head drives hard at this and Rohit Sharma gets a good hand to it at short cover as he saves a boundary for his team. A couple of runs taken here.
Fuller and on off, Travis Head blocks this out.
FOUR! Tucked it away nicely using the pace on offer. On a length angled at the pads, Travis Head stands tall and tucks this for a boundary toward deep mid wicket.
Short and wide outside off, Travis Head cuts this to point on a bounce.

OH NO! Edged and dropped. It is as easy as you could get as a keeper. On a length outside off, Travis Head tentatively pokes at this but gets an outside edge straight towards the keeper and Srikar Bharat drops a routine catch.
Dot to end the over as Head leaves this length delivery.
Fuller one outside off, Usman Khawaja stretches to poke but gets beaten.
On a length around off, Usman Khawaja defends this back to the bowler.
Fuller outside off, Usman Khawaja walks to the pitch of it and pushes this gently wide of Rohit at short cover for a single.
Back of a length around off, Travis Head punches this to short cover.
Fuller one swing in towards the batter, Travis Head punches this for no run.
Solidly defended off the front foot. On a length towards middle, Head defends this to short cover.
Fuller outside off, Usman Khawaja edges this on a couple of bounces toward gully.
On a length around off, Usman Khawaja defends this to the on side.
Full and wide of off, Usman Khawaja drives this through the cover region for a couple of runs.
Touch fuller outside off, Usman Khawaja leaves this for the keeper to collect.
Fuller and on middle, Usman Khawaja defends this back to the bowler.
Touch fuller keeping a tad low on off, Usman Khawaja does well to get some bat on this as it crawls towards third slip.
Fuller one outside off, Travis Head drives this to short cover.
Fuller around off, Travis Head pushes this to the off side for no run.
On a length outside off, Travis Head goes for an expensive drive but misses out.
Fuller one and on off, Travis Head punches this to mid off.
Back of a length on top of off, Travis Head cuts this to point.

FOUR! Sloppy work in the field by Umesh as he misfields one for a boundary. Fuller and on off, Travis Head gently goes of an on-drive straight to Umesh at mid on but he spills this and the ball has raced away for a boundary.
Tossed up outside off, Usman Khawaja pushes this to cover point.
Arm delivery flatter in trajectory and in middle, Usman Khawaja defends this out.
Gives it a bit more air, and beats Khawaja here as the ball has hit his pads. Loud appeal by India but the umpire turns this down.
Tossed up around off, Usman Khawaja defends this off the front foot.
Tossed up around pads, Usman Khawaja jumps down the track and pushes this to mid on.
Fuller one on middle, Usman Khawaja strides forward and blocks this out.
On a length just outside off, Travis Head punches this solidly to short cover.
Back of a length on top of off, Travis Head defends this off the front foot.
FOUR! Head is growing in confidence and this stroke proves that. Fuller one around off, Travis Head hits this through the line with extension of arms straight down the ground for a boundary.
On a length outside off, Travis Head cuts this to Axar Patel at point.
Head is opening up here. Short and wide outside off, Travis Head cuts this on a bounce to point.
FOUR! Glorious stroke and Head is up and running in this game now. Fuller outside off Travis Head drives this flawlessly through the cover region for yet another boundary.
Fuller one around middle, Usman Khawaja defends this.
2Tossed up around pads, Usman Khawaja tucks this wide of square leg for a couple of runs.
Length dragged back a bit, Usman Khawaja tucks this just in front of short leg.
Fuller around middle, Usman Khawaja pushes this to the on side.
Short in length around off, Usman Khawaja pushes this to mid off.
Fuller one around off, Usman Khawaja pushes this to mid on for no run.
Fuller around off, Travis Head pushes this to mid on for no run.
FOUR! Just outstanding hitting from the bat of Head. Short and close to off, Travis Head leans back and cuts this wide of Axar at point for a boundary.
On a length around pads, Travis Head pushes this to the on side for no run.
FOUR! He is imposing himself on the hosts here. On a length drifting down leg, Travis Head tucks this to fine leg for a boundary.
On a length outside off, Travis Head slogs but misses out.
FOUR! The third boundary of the over and Head is racing away here. On a length toward pads, Travis Head glances this in between mid on and mid-wicket for a boundary.
FOUR! India is under a bit of pressure here. Short in length around pads, Usman Khawaja flicks this off the back foot for a boundary towards fine leg.
Tossed up around off, Usman Khawaja defends this off the front foot.
Fuller one outside off, Usman Khawaja strides forward and blocks this out.
Gives it a bit more air and it skids off the surface onto the pads of Khawaja but this was going down leg.
Short in length around middle, Usman Khawaja tucks this to short mid wicket for no run.
Tossed up around middle, Usman Khawaja defends this to end the over.
Ravindra Jadeja begins with a shortish delivery bowled at the stumps. Travis Head knocks this back to the bowler.
Goes fuller this time and on the pads. Travis Head clips this through mid-wicket for a single.
Continues to bowl full and outside leg. Usman Khawaja dabs this towards short leg.
Floats this full and outside the off stump, Usman Khawaja blocks this to the right of the bowler.
FOUR! India leaking boundaries here! Ravindra Jadeja bowls this short and in line with the stumps. Usman Khawaja rocks back and pulls this towards deep backward square leg for four runs.
Tosses this one full and outside off. Usman Khawaja taps this towards point. 5 runs from Ravindra Jadeja's first over.
Ravichandran Ashwin floats this one full and outside off. Travis Head hits this hard but is stopped by the short cover fielder.
Loops this one full and outside the off stump. Travis Head knocks this to short cover.

OUT! CAUGHT! A wicket against the run of play and it is Ravichandran Ashwin who draws first blood! This is flighted full and on an off-stump line. Travis Head looks to be aggressive and shimmies down the wicket to get to the pitch of the ball. He looks to loft this over the man at mid on but gets the toe end of his bat. The ball lobs up to the left of Ravindra Jadeja who makes no mistake in getting low and grabbing hold of the ball. Australia lose their first wicket after a good opening partnership and Srikar Bharat will breathe a sigh of relief seeing Travis Head back in the shed.
Howout: c Ravindra Jadeja b Ravichandran Ashwin

Commentary: Tosses this one full and in line with the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne dabs this back down the pitch.
Strays onto the pads on a fuller length. Marnus Labuschagne clips this to the right of short fine leg and takes a single to get off the mark.
Gets this one to slide on with the arm on a fuller length and at the stumps. Usman Khawaja goes deep in the crease and blocks this out to the left of the bowler. End of a successful over for India.
Ravindra Jadeja floats this one full and in line with the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne pushes forward and gets an inside edge towards backward square leg.
Tosses this one full and attacks the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne defends this back to the bowler.
Continues to bowl at the stumps on a fuller length. Marnus Labuschagne gets forward to defend and gets an inside edge on his pads.
Loopy delivery bowled full and on a middle stump line. Marnus Labuschagne defends this solidly back to the bowler.
Bowls this one slightly short and just outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne goes deep in the crease and dabs this into the off side.
Fires this into the pads on a fuller length. Marnus Labuschagne clips this towards mid-wicket. A maiden over from Ravindra Jadeja.
Ravichandran Ashwin fires this on a shorter length and into the pads. Usman Khawaja rocks back and tucks this into the leg side.
Bowls this full and wide outside the off stump. Usman Khawaja leaves this one alone.
Attacks the stumps this time on a shortish length. Usman Khawaja uses the crease and defends this to short cover.
Flights this one full and bowls this outside off. Usman Khawaja gets tempted into the drive and hits it firmly to the short cover fielder.
This one stays a touch low on a fuller length and at the stumps. Usman Khawaja gets his bat down in time and keeps the ball out.
FOUR! Poor delivery and gets the treatment. Ravichandran Ashwin bowls this short and at the stumps. Usman Khawaja goes on the back foot and pulls this to deep square leg for four runs.
Ravindra Jadeja flights this full and outside off. Marnus Labuschagne blocks this towards cover.
Tosses this one full and outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne pushes this to mid off.
Loops this one wide outside off on a fuller length. Marnus Labuschagne knocks this to deep cover and takes a single.
Bowls this slightly short and outside off. Usman Khawaja stays back and dabs this into the off side.
Continues to bowl short and spinning into the stumps. Usman Khawaja tucks this towards mid-wicket.
Gets this at the stumps once again on a shortish length. Usman Khawaja flicks this into the leg side and keeps Ravindra Jadeja out.
Ravichandran Ashwin tosses this full and into the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne clips this to deep square leg and takes an easy single.
Floats this one into the stumps on a fuller length. Usman Khawaja defends this back to the bowler on his back foot.
Bowls this slightly short and outside the off stump. Usman Khawaja punches this towards mid off.
Gets this to skid in from outside off on a shorter length. Usman Khawaja blocks this solidly towards mid on.

FOUR! Great use of the wrists from Usman Khawaja! Ravichandran Ashwin strays onto the pads on a shorter length. Usman Khawaja uses the depth of the crease and whips this towards deep square leg for four more runs.
Goes full this time and outside the off pole. Usman Khawaja strokes this straight to the mid off fielder.
Ravindra Jadeja tosses this full and into the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne taps this back to the bowler.
Just outside the off pole on a fuller length. Marnus Labuschagne dabs this towards point.
Flights this full and in line with the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne defends this back towards the bowler.
Angles this into the pads on a fuller length. Marnus Labuschagne defends this to the right of the bowler.
Loopy delivery bowled outside the off pole on a fuller length. Marnus Labuschagne pushes this towards cover.
Goes full once again and into the pads. Marnus Labuschagne clips this to the fielder at mid on. Another maiden over from Ravindra Jadeja.
Ravichandran Ashwin bowls from over the wicket now and serves this full, just outside off. Usman Khawaja defends this back down the pitch towards the bowler.
Floats this one full as well and outside the leg stump. Usman Khawaja flicks this towards mid-wicket.
Tosses this full and on an off-stump line. Usman Khawaja gets his front foot forward and defends this into the leg side.
Bowls this one slightly short and in line with the stumps. Usman Khawaja goes back and clips this towards square leg.
Fires this one full and at the pads. Usman Khawaja gets his bat down and digs this out towards mid-wicket.
Flights this one full and just outside the off pole. Usman Khawaja eases this one towards mid on. Back-to-back maiden overs and India building some pressure here.
Mohammad Shami begins this spell with a fullish delivery served just outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne blocks this solidly to the left of the bowler.

OUT! CHOPPED ON! What an inspired bowling change this has been from India! Mohammad Shami strikes straight away and gets rid of the dangerous Marnus Labuschagne! This is bowled on a good length and outside the off pole. Marnus Labuschagne looks to play at the ball with no real conviction and ends up getting an inside edge.  The ball goes on to shatter the stumps and the Indians look ecstatic. Australia lose their second wicket and India are finding a way to claw themselves back into this game.
Bowls this one on a good length as well and angles this into the stumps from outside off. Steven Smith gets this towards the square leg off the inside edge of his and opens his account with a single.
Goes 'round the wicket to the left-hander and serves this full, outside off. Usman Khawaja gets a stride forward and blocks this towards point.
Continues to bowl full and angles this in from outside off. Usman Khawaja is solidly behind this one as he defends this towards mid off.
Attacks the stumps on a fuller length. Usman Khawaja is up to the task and he pushes this towards cover. A wicket and one run from this over and Mohammad Shami all of a sudden has his tail up.
Ravichandran Ashwin floats this one full and outside off. Steven Smith goes hard at the ball and mistimes it to the right of the bowler.
Goes full once again and in line with the stumps. Steven Smith defends this back to the bowler.
Tosses this one full and outside the off stump. Steven Smith blocks this towards mid off.
Beaten! Ravichandran Ashwin gets this one to keep it line on a fuller length and outside the off stump. Steven Smith pushes at this and the ball skims past his outside edge.
Bowls this slightly short and just outside the off stump. Steven Smith rocks back and dabs this towards mid-wicket.
Back to bowling full and outside the off stump. Steven Smith flicks this to the fielder at mid on. Ravichandran Ashwin follows up the wicket over with a maiden.
Mohammad Shami bowls this on a good length and outside the off stump from 'round the wicket. Usman Khawaja defends this towards mid off.
Goes full this time and outside off. Usman Khawaja digs this out back towards the bowler.
Angles this into the pads on a fuller length. Usman Khawaja gets his bat down and clips this towards mid on.
Continues to bowl full but serves this outside the off stump. Usman Khawaja blocks this solidly to the short cover fielder.
Strays onto the legs and bowls it full. Usman Khawaja misses out as he flicks this straight to the fielder at mid-wicket.
Bowls this one on a good length and into the stumps. Usman Khawaja gets behind the line of the ball and defends this towards mid on.
Ravichandran Ashwin bowls this full and in line with the stumps. Steven Smith goes deep in the crease and defends this back down the pitch.
A touch fuller this time and outside the off stump. Steven Smith pushes this to the left of the bowler.
Flighted delivery bowled full and just outside the off pole. Steven Smith clips this to deep mid-wicket and takes a single.
Tosses this one full and outside the off stump. Usman Khawaja gets a confident stride forward and defends this to the right of the bowler.
Bowls this one at the stumps on a shortish length. Usman Khawaja rocks back and tucks this to the left of mid-wicket for a run.
Loopy delivery bowled full and outside the off stump. Steven Smith gets forward but there is some extra bounce. The ball hits high on his bat and falls into the off side.
Mohammad Shami continues to bowl from 'round the wicket to the southpaw. He delivers this on a good length and angles this in from outside off. Usman Khawaja defends this back towards the bowler.
On a good length once again and outside the off stump. Usman Khawaja blocks this towards mid off.
Goes full this time and angles this into the pads. Usman Khawaja flicks this to the mid-wicket fielder.
Continues to bowl full and just outside the off pole. Usman Khawaja dabs this back down the pitch towards the bowler.
Tightens his line further with two close-in fielders on the leg side. Bowls this on a good length and at the stumps. Usman Khawaja taps this towards short mid-wicket.
Maiden over from Mohammad Shami! On a good length and on and off-stump line. Usman Khawaja knocks this back towards the bowler.
Ravichandran Ashwin floats this one full and outside the off stump from over the wicket. Steven Smith defends this back down the pitch.
Loops this one full and into the stumps. Steven Smith shimmies down the pitch and knocks this back to the bowler.
Floated full and outside the off stump. Steven Smith taps this back towards the bowler.
Attacks the stumps on a fuller length. Steven Smith pushes this back down the pitch towards Ravichandran Ashwin.
Goes 'round the wicket now and bowls this at the stumps on a shortish length. Steven Smith rocks back and tucks this towards mid-wicket.
Changes his mind and goes over the wicket once more. Bowls this full and outside the off stump. Steven Smith goes deep in the crease and blocks the ball out to play out another maiden.
Axar Patel will bowl the last over before Lunch and serves this full, in line with the stumps. Usman Khawaja defends this solidly.
Flights this full and outside off. Usman Khawaja keeps this one out solidly.
Goes wide to bowl this one and serves this full, outside off. Usman Khawaja continues to be watchful.
Loopy delivery bowled outside off on a fuller length. Usman Khawaja drives this straight to the cover fielder.
Goes 'round the wicket now and serves this full, at the stumps. Usman Khawaja gets an outside edge towards point.
Fires this into the pads on a fuller length. Usman Khawaja dabs this towards short mid-wicket. That will be LUNCH on DAY 1!
Ravindra Jadeja starts off with a full delivery into the stumps. Steven Smith clips this to the right of mid on and takes a run. Australia are off and running after the break.

FOUR! Really poor from Ravichandran Ashwin and Usman Khawaja accepts the gift gleefully! This is short and straying down leg. Usman Khawaja gets down on his knee and sweeps this to fine leg for four runs.
Bowls this slightly short and in line with the stumps. Usman Khawaja rocks back and pushes this to long on for a single.
Bowls this full and outside off. Steven Smith blocks this into the off side on his back foot.
Slightly short once again and on an off-stump line. Steven Smith taps this back down the pitch towards the bowler.
Ravindra Jadeja goes full this time and at the stumps. Steven Smith defends this back towards the bowler. 6 runs from the first over after Lunch.
Umesh Yadav bowls this full and onto the pads. Umesh Yadav clips this towards short-mid-wicket.
Bowls this one slightly back on a length and in line with the stumps. Usman Khawaja stands tall and tucks this towards the fielder at short mid-wicket.
Delivers this one on a good length and attacks the stumps. Usman Khawaja dabs this back down the pitch.
Continues to bowl at the stumps on a good length. Usman Khawaja is well behind the line of the ball as he keeps it out.
Strays onto the pads on a good length. Usman Khawaja flicks this down to fine leg and collects a single.
Goes a fraction fuller this time and outside the off pole. Steven Smith dabs this towards cover.
Ravindra Jadeja floats this full and outside the off stump, Usman Khawaja pushes this towards mid off.

FOUR! Great use of the crease by Usman Khawaja! Ravindra Jadeja bowls this one short and in line with the leg stump. Usman Khawaja goes deep into the crease in a flash and pulls this towards deep square leg for four runs.
Goes full and into the stumps. Usman Khawaja dabs this back towards the bowler.
Flights this one full as well and just outside the off pole. Usman Khawaja blocks this out solidly.
Fires this one quicker and at the off pole. Usman Khawaja is on the back foot and gets his bat down in time to keep the ball out.
Bowls this one short and in line with the stumps. Usman Khawaja goes back and pulls once again but there is a fielder in the deep now and he gets a single to deep backward square leg.
Umesh Yadav bowls this on a good length and in line with the stumps, Usman Khawaja defends this back down the wicket.
A low full toss this time served outside off. Usman Khawaja works this to deep point and takes a comfortable single.
Delivers this on a good length and outside the off stumps. Steven Smith gets across the stumps and defends this towards cover-point.
Goes full this time and outside the off pole. Steven Smith dabs this towards mid off.
Continues to bowl full and outside the off stump. Steven Smith drives this straight to the fielder at cover.
This is served outside off on a fuller length. Steven Smith gets his bat behind the ball and taps this towards cover.
Ravindra Jadeja comes over the wicket and bowls this short, going down leg. Usman Khawaja pulls this to deep backward square leg and collects one.
From over the wicket to the right-hander. Bowls this full and outside off. Steven Smith blocks this back to the bowler.
Slightly short and outside off. Steven Smith pushes this towards point and takes a run.
Fires this one full and into the stumps. Usman Khawaja keeps the ball out.
Loops this one full and outside off. Usman Khawaja dabs this towards cover.
Continues to flight this full and outside off. Usman Khawaja is watchful and he taps this towards cover-point.
Umesh Yadav bowls this on a good length and into the stumps. Steven Smith clips this towards mid-wicket.
On a good length once again and on the pads. Steven Smith flicks this to the fielder at mid-wicket.

FOUR! Great hands from Steven Smith and he plays a classy shot to the fence! Umesh Yadav bowls this back of a length and outside off. Steven Smith stands tall and eases this to deep point for four runs.
Goes back to bowling on a good length and just outside the off pole. Steven Smith defends this towards the cover fielder.
Continues bowling on a good length and outside the off stump. Steven Smith leaves this one alone and is unhappy with something near the sight screen.
Goes full and into the stumps. Steven Smith clips this towards the man placed at short mid-wicket. The crowd gets excited as they think it is a catch.
Ravindra Jadeja fires this one full and into the stumps. Usman Khawaja is on the back foot but manages to keep this out.
Floats this one full and outside off. Usman Khawaja gets forward this time and defends this back towards the bowler.
Slightly short and straying onto the pads. Usman Khawaja rocks back and flicks this towards deep square leg for a single.
Bowls this short and at the stumps. Steven Smith dabs this to the right of the bowler.
On a shortish length once again and outside the off stump. Steven Smith pushes this towards cover-point.
Tosses this one full and just outside the off pole. Steven Smith defends this solidly towards cover.
Umesh Yadav bowls this on a good length and on an off-stump line. Usman Khawaja gets behind the line of the ball and blocks this solidly.
Goes a fraction fuller and outside the off stump. Usman Khawaja mistimes his drive towards mid off.
This is bowled full once again and at the stumps. Usman Khawaja digs this out back down the pitch towards the bowler.
Continues to attack the stumps on a fuller length. Usman Khawaja keeps this out as well as he knocks it back towards Umesh Yadav.
Goes 'round the wicket now and angles this into the stumps from outside off. Usman Khawaja punches this past the bowler for a single.
On a good length from over the wicket, outside the off pole. Steven Smith defends this solidly into the off side.
Ravichandran Ashwin flights this one full and outside off. Usman Khawaja drives but the ball is stopped by the short cover fielder.
Bowls this one full and angles this into the stumps. Usman Khawaja blocks this towards short cover.
Flights this one full and just outside the off pole. Usman Khawaja defends this towards mid off.
Floats this one into the stumps on a fuller length. Usman Khawaja dabs this to the right of the bowler on his back foot.
Slightly short and bowled into the stumps. Usman Khawaja goes back into the crease and clips this towards mid-wicket.
Loopy delivery bowled full and outside off. Usman Khawaja pushes this to the right of the bowler. Ravichandran Ashwin starts off this spell with a maiden.
Axar Patel begins with a full delivery fired into the stumps. Steven Smith blocks this towards cover.
Floats this one full and in line with the stumps. Steven Smith dabs this into the off side.
Loopy delivery bowled full and outside off. Steven Smith drives the ball hard and Rohit Sharma does well to stop this at covers.
Flights this one full and outside the off pole. Steven Smith eases this to the left of mid off and takes a single.
Tosses this one full and outside off. Usman Khawaja defends this to the right of the bowler who is coming from over the wicket.
Bowls this one full as well and angles this in from outside off. Usman Khawaja is solidly behind this one as he taps it back towards the bowler.
Ravichandran Ashwin flights this full and in line with the stumps. Steven Smith defends this towards mid-wicket.
Tosses this full and at the stumps. Steven Smith dabs this back towards the bowler.
Loopy delivery bowled full and outside off. Steven Smith blocks this to the left of the bowler.
Slightly short and on a leg-stump line. Steven Smith taps this towards short leg.
Flights this full and into the pads. Steven Smith clips this towards deep square leg for a run.
Tosses this one into the stumps on a fuller length. Usman Khawaja smothers this back down the pitch.
Axar Patel floats this full and into the stumps. Steven Smith defends this back towards the bowler.
Slightly short and outside off. Steven Smith stands tall and pushes this towards short cover.

OUT! BOWLED! Ravindra Jadeja strikes and India have got rid of the opponent skipper who was looking untroubled at the wicket! This is bowled full and outside the off stump. Steven Smith looks to block this into the off side but gets an inside edge back that hits his pads and rolls onto the stumps. A massive sigh of relief from India as Steven Smith hangs his head down in disappointment. Just the breakthrough the hosts needed to start this session and they will now look to put some pressure on the new batter.
Fuller around middle, Peter Handscomb defends this to the on side and gets a single.
Fuller around off, Usman Khawaja defends this of the front foot. End of a successful over for India.
On a length outside off, Peter Handscomb pushes this to short cover.

Yorker nailed to perfection. Peter Handscomb defends this well.
Well directed bouncer body bound, Peter Handscomb ducks away from this.

FOUR! Peter Handscomb plays this really well and finds the fence. Bouncer around head, Peter pulls this wide of the fielder at deep square leg for a boundary.
FOUR! Peter has come out with a positive mindset as he pulls another attempted bouncer in front of the square this time for yet another boundary.
Short in length around middle, Usman Khawaja pushes this to square leg for a single.

OUT! BOWLED! What a happy sight it is for any fast bowler to see the off pole cartwheel towards the wicket-keeper! This is bowled on a good length and just outside the off pole. The ball reverses a bit and that is enough to beat the outside edge of the bat. The ball uproots the stump and Peter Handscomb's enterprising inning comes to an end. Australia lose their fourth wicket and India are finding a way to keep themselves alive in this game.
Fuller around off, Cameron Green defends this off the front foot.
On a length outside off, Cameron Green leaves this for the keeper to collect.
FOUR! Khawaja finds the gap and plays this well for a boundary. Full and wide outside off, Usman Khawaja drives this through cover for a boundary.
Short in length outside off, Usman Khawaja defends this to silly point.
Fuller around pads, Usman Khawaja defends this off the front foot.

Short in length around off, Usman Khawaja pushes this to mid off.

FOUR! Slightly overpitched and Khawaj latches onto it. Overpitched outside off, Usman Khawaja drives this through the cover region for a boundary.
Short in length around off, Khawaja tucks this to fine leg for a couple.
Fuller and on off, Usman Khawaja defends this off the front foot.

On off stump, kept out.
Yet another maiden and Australia are going nowhere at the moment. Quicker and flatter on off stump, solidly blocked out by Cameron Green.
Goes a bit wider of the crease and drifts it in from outside off, Usman Khawaja blocks it out.
A hint of flight as this is drifted onto middle and leg, Usman Khawaja defends it out with soft hands.
Nagging length around middle, Khawaja is just happy to defend off the front foot.

Starts off with a fullish delivery outside off, Cameron Green drives it through the cover region and picks up a couple of runs.
On a hard length and on the body, Green nudges it down in front of mid-wicket.
FOUR! Slashed away! A real loosener outside off, with not much pace behind it either. Cameron Green waits on the back foot and cuts it late into the backward point fence.
Short and outside off, Cameron Green hops and cuts it to the right of the man at deep backward point for a couple of runs.
FOUR! Lovely drive! This is full and straight, Cameron Green drives it dead straight past the bowler and the ball runs away into the fence for another boundary.
Good length around the top of off, Green keeps it down on the deck. 12 off the first over with the second new ball, a fruitful one for Australia.
Steams in from around the wicket and angles in a length ball from around off. Usman Khawaja blocks it out on the off side.
On a good length around off, this is dabbed away toward cover-point.

BYE! On a hard length outside off, the ball seams away after leaving the batter and the keeper Srikar Bharat fails to collect it cleanly. The ball trickles toward third man but the fielder from first slip cuts it off and keeps it down to a run.
Switches to over the wicket and angles in a fuller delivery onto middle, Cameron Green blocks it out.
Good length around off, Green crouches a bit and pushes it toward cover-point for a single.
FOUR! Easy pickings for Usman Khawaja and he moves into the 90s. This is full and angled on the pads, Khawaja clips it away into the vacant square leg fence.
Comes from around the wicket and bowls it full on middle, Cameron Green prods and defends.
Tossed up around middle, Green defends it out.
Drops it short now and bowls it around leg stump, Cameron Green works it away past square leg and picks up a run.
Nicely drifted from outside off and on a nagging length as well, Usman Khawaja doesn't play at it.
A tad shorter and on the pads, Usman Khawaja flicks it down to fine leg and comes back for two with ease.
A tad shorter outside off, Khawaja eases it off the back foot in front of the man at point for another brace.
FOUR! Put away with disdain! Short of a length outside off, Cameron Green stands tall and muscles it away through wide mid on for a cracking boundary.
Fullish length around off, driven on the up but straight to extra cover.

In the air... lands safely! Mohammad Shami gets this one kick off a shortish length and Cameron Green is caught on the back foot. Green tries to get behind it and only manages to lob it off the handle of the bat in front of short cover. There is no one there and the ball lands safely.
Banged in short and around off, Cameron Green looks to pull but ends up dragging it in front of mid-wicket. Ravichandran Ashwin there gives the chase and keeps it down to a couple of runs.
FOUR! Looking for the yorker but ends up being a low full toss on off stump, Cameron Green drills it past mid off and the ball sprints away into the fence.
A bumper now over the stumps, Cameron Green plays a cracking pull shot toward deep mid-wicket and picks up a single.
Tosses it up full and around off, Green strokes it back to the bowler.
Holds it back a touch and flights it on off stump, Cameron Green blocks it off the front foot.
Slows it up again and bowls it a bit shorter on the pads, Cameron Green nudges it toward mid-wicket.
Tossed up on middle, this is driven through mid on for a single.
Flighted delivery, on a nagging length around off, Usman Khawaja leans forward and blocks it out.
A fraction shorter and on the stumps, Khawaja goes on the back foot to defend.
Starts off with a full ball on off stump, Cameron Green drives it along the ground to long off for one.
Flatter and around off, kept out off the back foot.
Round-arm delivery, on a nagging length and outside off, Usman Khawaja goes on the back foot to keep this one out.
On the pads, flicked away through square leg for a single.
Flatter delivery, Green mistimes the drive toward extra cover.
Drifts it onto the off stump, Cameron Green stays solid in defense.
Fraction shorter and around off, this is played off the back foot and with soft hands to the left of cover-point for an easy single.
Gives it more air and bowls it a touch shorter on middle, Cameron Green keeps it down in front of short leg.
Nagging length, angling just down the leg side, Green misses the flick and there's half an appeal for caught behind.
FOUR! Another lovely shot from Cameron Green! Floated up outside off, Green gets down on one knee and creams it through covers for a boundary.
Flatter one around middle, kept out.
Tossed up full and on middle, nicely driven through mid on for a single.
FOUR! Green has not shut a shot here. Shor and wide outside of the off-stump, Cameron Green bottom edges this as he attempts this cut and earns a boundary.
Fuller outside off, Cameron Green defends this to the off side.
Fuller outside off, Usman Khawaja guides this to off side for a single.
Fuller around middle, Usman Khawaja defends this in front.
Fuller around pads, Usman Khawaja tucks this to short mid wicket for no run.
Short in length around pads, Usman Khawaja flicks this to deep square leg for a single as he edges closer to his century.

FOUR! Century for Usman Khawaja and what a sensational knock this has been. His maiden ton in India and against them. Fuller on his pads, Usman Khawaja flicks this out in the vacant square leg region for a boundary before leaping up and punching the air in joy.
On a length outside off, Usman Khawaja defends this to the off side.
On a length outside off, Usman Khawaja looks to defend but gets beaten on the outside edge.
Full and wide outside off, Usman Khawaja leaves this for the keeper to collect.
Fuller around off, Usman Khawaja pushes this to point for no run.
Usman Khawaja gets a single to end the day. On a length angling in towards him, Khawaja pushes this wide of short mid wicket and takes a single. That will be Stumps on Day 1!
Ravindra Jadeja starts with a tossed up delivery, full and on middle, turning in, Usman Khawaja blocks it down the pitch.
Flatter, short and on leg, Usman Khawaja moves back and nudges it through square leg for a single.
Floated, full and on middle, Cameron Green looks defend it on the front foot, but misses and gets hit on the pads.
Flighted, full and on off, Cameron Green pushes it towards short covers.

FIFTY FOR GREEN! A fine knock from him and he has played really well, but he will look to make it big now. This is short and on middle, keeps low too, Cameron Green knocks it towards long off for a run.
A single to end the over as this short delivery is flicked off the back foot towards deep square leg by Usman Khawaja.
Axar Patel begins with a short delivery, on middle, Usman Khawaja tucks it towards short mid-wicket.
Floated, short and on middle, Usman Khawaja keeps it out on the pitch.
Another short delivery, on middle, Usman Khawaja gets surprised by the extra bounce, but fends it down towards short leg.
Axar Patel continues to bowl short, on leg this time, Usman Khawaja works it through square leg for a run.
Tossed up, full and on off, Cameron Green drives it towards mid off and scampers across for another run.
Flighted, full and on off, Usman Khawaja decides to come forward, but in the end stays on his crease and defends it to the leg side.
Mohammad Shami starts with a good-length delivery, on middle, shaping in, Cameron Green looks to play at it, but gets an inside edge towards deep square leg for a single.
Goes a bit fuller and on middle, keeps low, Usman Khawaja tries to defend, but gets an outside edge along the ground towards third man for a run.
Full again and on off, Cameron Green opens the face of his bat and guides it through point for another run.
On a length and on off, Usman Khawaja pushes it towards short covers.

EDGED BUT SAFE! Mohammad Shami pitches this up on the fifth stump line, Usman Khawaja looks to drive it away, but gets an outside edge. However, the ball does not carry and goes on two bounces towards Srikar Bharat behind the stumps.
Fullish again and on middle, angling in, Usman Khawaja knocks it back to the bowler.
Tossed up, full and on off, Cameron Green drives it towards mid off for a single.
Floated, full and on middle, Usman Khawaja defends it on the front foot.
Slower through the air, on off, Usman Khawaja leans on and blocks it out.
Flatter, full and on middle, Usman Khawaja drills it to the left of the bowler.
A bit short and on off, Usman Khawaja tucks it towards short mid-wicket.
Short again and on middle, Usman Khawaja moves back and clips it towards deep mid-wicket for a ru.
This is on a good length and outside off, Usman Khawaja decides to leave it alone.
Fuller and on middle, Usman Khawaja works it towards mid on.
Full again and on middle, Usman Khawaja tucks it towards mid on.
Overpitched and on middle, Usman Khawaja drives it towards mid off.
This is pitched up, on middle, Usman Khawaja drills it past the bowler and in between mid off and mid on for an easy single.
Another pitched-up delivery, on off, Cameron Green drives straight to mid off.
Tossed up, full and on off, Usman Khawaja strides forward and defends it.
Flatter and around off, Usman Khawaja stays back and keeps it out.
Floated, full and on off, Usman Khawaja drives it towards short covers.
Shortish and on middle, Usman Khawaja stays back and blocks it down the pitch.
Flighted, full and around off, Usman Khawaja thinks about playing it, but withdraws his bat at the last moment.
Shorter in length and on the leg stump line, Usman Khawaja moves back and nudges it towards deep square leg for a single.
On a length and on middle, Usman Khawaja knocks it back towards the bowler.
Full and outside off, Usman Khawaja lets it go to the keeper.
Full again and on off, Usman Khawaja drives it straight to short covers.
Mohammad Shami pitches it up, on off, Usman Khawaja defends it on the front foot towards mid off.
Overpitched and well outside off, Usman Khawaja makes an easy leave.
Maiden over! Mohammad Shami continues to bowler fuller, on middle, Usman Khawaja drills it wide of mid off, but for no run.
Floated, full and on middle, Cameron Green turns it towards short mid-wicket.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Cameron Green leans on and blocks it down the pitch.
Angles ths is one into the batter, short and on leg, Cameron Green keeps it out to the off side.
Flatter, full and on middle, Cameron Green defends it back to the bowler.
On middle, blocked out.
Quicker one, short and on leg, angling in, Cameron Green stays back and tries to flick it away, but misses and gets hit on the pads.
Ravichandran Ashwin begins with a flatter delivery, full and on off, Usman Khawaja pushes it towards short covers.
Floated, full and on off, Usman Khawaja stays back and defends it to the off side.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Usman Khawaja blocks it back to the bowler.
Shortish and on off, Usman Khawaja moves back and steers it towards point.
Fligthed, full and on off, Usman Khawaja drives it towards short covers.
Gives this one some air, on off, swinging in, Usman Khawaja eases it towards long off for a single.
Short and on middle, Usman Khawaja moves back and tucks it to the right of square leg for a quick single.
Tossed up, full and on off, Cameron Green knocks it towards silly mid off.
Floated, full and on middle, Cameron Green fends it off the inner half towards square leg.
Flighted, full and on middle, Cameron Green leans on and blocks it down the pitch.
Quicker, full and on middle, Cameron Green once again gets an inside edge towards square leg as he tries to keep it out.
Sligtly shorter and on off, Cameron Green goes on the front foot and pushes it towards short covers.
Flatter one, angling in from around middle, Usman Khawaja goes on the back foot to keep it out.
Slows it up a bit and slides it onto the pads, Khawaja nudges it with soft hands toward square leg.
Shorter one on off, this is eased down to long off for a single. The 100-run stand is up between these two as well.
Pushed through quicker and on leg stump, Cameron Green blocks it back to the bowler.
FOUR! Put away with ease! Too short and too wide from Ashwin, Cameron Green waits on the back foot and cuts it hard through the point region for a boundary.
Tossed up, full and on the legs, Green whips it to deep mid-wicket for a single.
Angled into middle and leg, Green blocks it out with soft hands.
A bit more round arm and angling into middle, Cameron Green strides forward to defend.
Fired in on middle, kept out by Green.
Quicker one around off, Green keeps it out on the off side.
A bit flatter and on the pads, tucked away to short mid-wicket.
Bowls it on off stump, Green solidly defends it off the front foot. Maiden!
Floated up on a nagging length around off, Usman Khawaja defends from deep inside the crease.
Flighted delivery, angling onto the pads, Khawaja works it in front of square leg and rotates the strike.
Floated across the right-hander, Cameron Green strides out and drives it through extra cover for a single.
Gets it to drift in a bit from around off, Usman Khawaja blocks it toward cover.
This is drifted onto middle, Usman Khawaja prods and makes the block.
Fraction shorter and on the pads, Khawaja works it 'round the corner for a run.
Umesh Yadav starts a new spell from around the wicket and angles in a good-length delivery onto middle. Usman Khawaja pushes it gently to the right of mid on and scampers through for one.
Goes over the wicket now to the right-hander and angles in another length ball around the top of off. Cameron Green taps it in front of point and picks up a single.
FOUR! Easy pickings! Slightly shorter and on the pads, Usman Khawaja flicks it off his hips and finds the vacant square leg fence.
On a good length around off, Usman Khawaja eases it toward cover-point.
Umesh Yadav bangs this short but way down the leg side, Usman Khawaja offers no shot at it.
Back of a length and around off, Khawaja hangs back and steers it down to third man for one.
Nagging length outside off and keeping a bit low, Khawaja defends it off the back foot.
Nicely flighted outside off, trying to entice the batter but Usman Khawaja leaves it alone.
This is full and outside off, Khawaja drives it sweetly toward sweeper cover for a single.
On a shorter length and on middle, Green blocks it out.
A bit flatter and tries to angle it across the off stump, Green stays deep in his crease and blocks it back on the deck.
Fuller and on the stumps, pushed firmly back past the bowler down to long on for a run.
Good length outside off, Cameron Green plays the cover drive on the up and times it well. Ravindra Jadeja at extra cover does well to make a half-stop to his left and keeps it down to a single.

FOUR! Umesh Yadav gets his line wrong again and Usman Khawaja takes full advantage of it. A touch shorter on leg stump, Khawaja hops back and tucks it away in between deep square leg and deep backward square leg for a boundary.
Keeps the length short and bowls it around the hips, this is wristed away to deep backward square leg for one.
Back of a good length around off, hit away on the up but straight to the man at extra cover.
Shortish length outside off, Cameron Green looks to slap it away off the back foot but loses his shape a bit and mistimes it toward covers.
Fuller one angled into the pads, Cameron Green flicks it away in front of square on the leg side for a couple of runs.
Comes from over the wicket to the left-hander now and floats one down leg, Usman Khawaja hangs back and pads it away.
Slightly slower and shorter around leg, Usman Khawaja waits on the back foot and works it through square leg for one.
Back to around the wicket now and tries to slide across a quicker one, Green defends it off the front foot.
Floated up around leg stump, Cameron Green strides forward and makes the block.
Just pulls back the length a bit and flights it on the off stump, Green stays solid in defense.
A touch shorter on off stump, kept out by Green.
Comes from around the wicket and angles in a full ball from around off, Usman Khawaja pushes it toward extra cover.
Fullish length, in that channel around off and angling in late. Usman Khawaja makes an assured leave.
Length ball, pushed a bit wider of the off stump, Khawaja stays back and dabs it down toward gully.
Pitches this one up on the off stump, Usman Khawaja shuffles across a bit and blocks it out.
Nagging length, on a tight line around the off stump, Usman Khawaja goes deep in his crease to keep this one out.

FOUR! In control! On a length angling in from outside off, Usman Khawaja hangs back and edges it down with soft hands through the slip cordon and the ball races away into the third man fence. The 300 is now up for Australia.
Floated on middle and leg, Cameron Green leans forward and pushes it down to long on for a single.
This is drifted in fuller and onto middle and off, Usman Khawaja goes back and across to keep this one out on the off side.
Shorter and on off stump, Khawaja punches it toward mid off.
Quicker one, on a nagging length and angling onto middle, Khawaja defends it from deep in his crease.
Tosses it up a bit and bowls it around off, Usman Khawaja blocks it off the front foot toward cover.
This is floated full and on the fifth stump line, Usman Khawaja watches the ball go through to the keeper.
FOUR! Lovely timing! On a length around off, Cameron Green gets on the front foot and punches it on the up and off the middle of the bat through extra cover for a boundary.
Good length, angling into middle and leg, Green defends it from inside his crease.
On a good length and over middle, this is played off the back foot straight to short mid-wicket.
On a hard length, angling onto the body, Green stays back and tucks it away in front of square leg for an easy single.
This is bowled full and angled onto the off stump, Usman Khawaja blocks it out.
Full again around off, Usman Khawaja drives it sweetly but straight to mid off.
Floated, full and on off, Cameron Green leans on and blocks it wide of short covers.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Cameron Green looks defend, but the extra bounce hits the sticker of the bat and rolls towards the bowler.
Flighted, full and on middle, Cameron Green negotiates it well.
Gives this some air, on off, Cameron Green keeps it out to the off side.
Flatter, full and on leg, keeps low too, Cameron Green tries to flick it away, but misses and gets hit on the pads as the ball goes nowhere.
A maiden over! This is looped up, full and on off, Cameron Green pushes it towards silly mid off.
Overpitched and outside off, tempts the batter to drive, but Usman Khawaja lets it go to the keeper.
On a length and on middle, Usman Khawaja knocks it towards mid on.
Pitched up, on middle, angling in, Usman Khawaja moves across a bit and works it towards mid on again.
Fuller one and on middle, Usman Khawaja blocks it back to the bowler.
This is on a good length and around off, Usman Khawaja opens the face of his bat and steers it through point for a single.
Goes fuller and on leg, angling in, Cameron Green keeps it out towards short mid-wicket.

FOUR! Almost a wicket for Jadeja! This is tossed up, full and on off, turning in sharply, Usman Khawaja tries to drive on the up, but gets an inside edge just past the stumps and Srikar Bharat fails to get behind as well and the ball races to the fine leg fence for a boundary.
Floated, full and on off again, Usman Khawaja pads it away.
Flatter, full and on off, Usman Khawaja stays back and blocks it out.
Flighted, full and on off, straightens after hitting the deck, Usman Khawaja leans on to defend, but gets beaten on the outside edge.
Darts this one full and on middl, Usman Khawaja works it towards square leg.
Looped up, full and on off, Usman Khawaja drives it firmly through covers for a couple of runs. End of an eventful over!
FOUR! Lovely shot! Umesh Yadav serves this full and on off, Cameron Green shows the full face of the bat and drives it wide of mid off for a boundary.
On a length and on middle, Cameron Green keeps it out to the leg side.
Goes a bit fuller and on middl, Cameron Green knocks it towards silly mid on.
FOUR! Easy pickings for Green! Umesh Yadav attempts the yorker, but bowls a low full toss on off, Cameron Green thrashes it through covers for another boundary.
Pitched up and on leg, Cameron Green tucks it towards short mid-wicket.

FOUR! Another expensive over from Umesh Yadav! He bowls this full again and on off, Cameron Green stays in his creases and drills it with sweet timing through covers for the third boundary of the over.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Usman Khawaja prods forward and blocks it out.
Floated, full and on off, turning in, Usman Khawaja moves back and defends it back to the bowler.
A bit short and on off, Usman Khawaja moves across and keeps it out to the off side.
Flatter, full and outside off, Usman Khawaja drives it through cover-point as Axar Patel chases it down and does well to keep it inside. Three runs taken!
Slower through the air, on off, Cameron Green pushes it towards silly mid off.
Gives this one some air as well, on off, Cameron Green is already on the front foot and plays it towards silly mid off again.
Shortish and around off, Usman Khawaja waits for it and guides it towards third man for a single.
Floated, full and on off, Cameron Green pushes it towards short covers.
Slower through the air, on middle, Cameron Green prods forward and blocks it out.
Shorter in length and on off, Cameron Green stays back and slaps it towards long off for a run.
Flatter, full and on off, Usman Khawaja opens the face of his bat and steers it through backward point for one.
Tossed up, full and on off, Cameron Green blocks it to the left of the bowler.
Mohammad Shami tries for the bouncer, on off, angling in, did not bounce that much, Usman Khawaja sways away from it.
This is on a good length and on middle, angling in sharply, Usman Khawaja looks to work it away, but misses and gets hit on his thigh pads.
Back of a length and outside off, Usman Khawaja punches it towards deep point for a single.
Goes a bit fuller and on the pads, Cameron Green tickles it towards fine leg for a run.

FOUR! 150 FOR KHAWAJA! Mohammad Shami lands this short but down the leg side, Usman Khawaja swivels and hooks it towards the fine leg fence for a boundary. He will be eying for that double hundred now.
This is on a hard length and on middle, Usman Khawaja dabs it down towards mid on.
Short and on leg, Cameron Green moves back and flicks it through mid-wicket for a single.
Tossed up, full and on off, Usman Khawaja blocks it to the right of the bowler.
Shortish and on off, Usman Khawaja stays back and keeps it out down the pitch.
Floated, full and on off, Usman Khawaja drives it wide of short covers where the fielder dives to his right to stop it.
Flatter, full and on leg, Usman Khawaja nudges it towards square leg.
Slightly shorter and on middle, Usman Khawaja defends it on the back foot.

FOUR! Nice shot! Mohammad Shami set up the field for a bouncer and he delivers it as well, but around off, Cameron Green picks up the length early and pulls it hard towards the deep mid-wicket fence for a boundary.
On a length and on middle, Cameron Green blocks it back to the bowler.

EDGED AND FOUR! Mohammad Shami lands this on a hard length and on middle, nips away a bit, Cameron Green looks to block it without much footwork, and gets a thick outside edge. However, there is only a third slip in place and this goes well wide of him and towards the third man fence for a boundary. Green moves to 94!
Fuller and on middle, Cameron Green pushes it wide of mid on for a quick single.
Overpitched and on off, Usman Khawaja drives it towards mid off.
A slower delivery, on a length and on middle, Usman Khawaja keeps it out towards mid on. THAT WILL BE LUNCH ON DAY 2!
Starts off with a tossed-up delivery on middle and leg, Cameron Green pushes it back to the bowler.
A bit flatter and on off stump, Green eases it toward cover.
Slightly flighted and drifting it in from around off stump, Green blocks it out.
Floated up on the off stump, this is knocked down to long off for a single.
A touch shorter and turning it in from outside off, Usman Khawaja covers the line and edges it down with soft hands toward short third man for a single.
Just a hint of turn as this is bowled around the off stump, Cameron Green blocks it off the front foot.
This is bowled full and wide, angling well across the batter. Usman Khawaja leaves it alone.
Length ball right on the money, Khawaja gets his bat down in time and defends it toward mid on.
A touch shorter and over the leg stump, Khawaja hops and flicks it to short mid-wicket.
This is pitched up around middle, Usman Khawaja with a gentle push back past the bowler for a quick single.
Pitches it up on the off stump, Cameron Green drives it nicely off the front foot but straight to extra cover.
Keeps it full and pushes it wider, this is driven again but straight to Cheteshwar Pujara at covers.
Shorter in length and bowled on the off pole, Usman Khawaja pushes it off the back foot down to long on for a run.

FOUR! Cut away and that will be a maiden Test hundred for Cameron Green! A sensational knock from the young man and he is absolutely delighted and rightly so. Green takes off the helmet and soaks in the applause from the crowd and the dressing room. The ball is bowled slightly shorter and outside off, Green waits on the back foot and cuts it hard wide of backward point for a boundary.
Angled into middle, Cameron Green pushes it gently to the right of the bowler.
Flatter one around off, kept out on the off side.
This is bowled quicker, trying to slide one into the off pole but Green stays watchful in defense.
Pushed through on the off stump, Green pushes it toward extra cover.
Length ball on middle, staying a touch low. Usman Khawaja hops back and works it away in front of mid-wicket for one.
Pitches this one up on the off stump, Cameron Green solidly defends it off the front foot.
Good length around the top of off, Green pushes at it and plays it in front of cover-point for a single.

Risky single but they get through! Fullish length on middle and leg, Usman Khawaja pushes it to the left of mid on and sets off for the single. Ravindra Jadeja there picks it up and fires in a throw at the bowler's end but misses. Khawaja was safe even if that had hit the stumps.
On a hard length outside off, dabbed down to the right of the gully fielder.
FOUR! Uppish but in the gap! Fullish length outside off and shaping away a touch, Cameron Green leans on and drives it uppishly through extra cover and picks up a boundary.
Slowed up on a shorter length and angled in from outside off. Usman Khawaja shuffles across and keeps it out.
Floated up around off, this is driven all along the ground to long on for a single.
On middle, looking to turn it away, Green blocks it out.
A bit slower and around off, Green makes another block off the front foot.
FOUR! Powered away and runs are flowing here for Australia. This is full and outside off, Cameron Green drives it firmly and a bit uppishly through the cover region for another boundary.
This is bowled around off, Green knocks it down to long off and picks up a single.
This is pitched up on middle and leg, Green blocks it back to the bowler.
Length ball angling into the pads, Cameron Green works it to short mid-wicket.
Goes full and on off stump, Cameron Green drives it on the up but finds the fielder at mid off.
Fullish length on the legs, flicked away through mid-wicket for an easy single.
Pitched-up delivery on leg stump, Usman Khawaja plays a straight drive off the middle of the blade but hits it straight to mid on.
A single to end and the 200-run partnership is up between these two, a mighty effort. Back of a length around off, Usman Khawaja stays back and eases it in front of cover-point for a run.
Loops this one up on the off stump, Usman Khawaja pushes it back to the bowler.
Flatter one around off, staying a touch low. Khawaja backs away and pushes it through the cover region for a couple of runs.
Flighted, on a nagging length around off and just turning in a bit. Usman Khawaja shuffles and gets behind the line to make the block.
Bowls it flatter and around off, Khawaja defends it off the back foot.
This one is angled into middle stump, Khawaja makes another block.
Fraction shorter and on off stump, Usman Khawaja gets behind the line of the ball and keeps it out.
Starts off with a floater down the leg side, Cameron Green looks to flick and misses. The keeper whips off the bails but Green manages to keep his back leg planted inside the crease.
Flatter one around leg stump, Cameron Green strides out and pads it away.
Nicely flighted on middle and leg, Cameron Green leans on and works it through mid-wicket for a run.
Slower and shorter, angling into middle and leg, Khawaja has all the time in the world to get on the back foot and blocks it out.
Gives it a big loop and floats it outside off, Usman Khawaja plays a flowing cover drive to sweeper cover and picks up a single.
Tossed up on middle and leg, Green strides forward to defend.
A huge roar from the crowd who are trying to get the hosts a bit pumped up. This is bowled on off stump, Khawaja pushes it out on the off side.
Shorter in length and around off, Khawaja gets on the back foot and blocks it out.
Angling into middle, blocked out once again.
This is pushed through a bit fuller and quicker on middle, Khawaja pushes it gently toward mid on.
Flatter and on the pads, Khawaja rocks back to work it toward square leg.

An appeal for LBW but nothing from the umpire. Rohit Sharma does take the review, the first one of the game and it seems like a shot in the dark. No shot is offered by Usman Khawaja which means the third umpire will directly go to Ball Tracking and the impact won't matter either. The replays show that the ball is missing the off stump by a long way. Coming to the delivery, it is bowled a bit shorter and well outside off, Usman Khawaja gets his front pad out and blocks it away toward point.
Tossed up on the stumps, Cameron Green blocks it out.
Full and around middle, knocked down the ground for a single.
Flatter and close to the off stump, Usman Khawaja defends it off the back foot.
A bit fuller and around off, this is pushed away to cover.
Loops this one up, full and outside off, enticing the batter but Usman Khawaja just leaves it alone.
This is the carrom ball, bowled full and around off, Usman Khawaja drives it square of the wicket to deep cover-point and picks up a single.
Bowled full and drifted onto middle and off, Khawaja plays it off the front foot back to the bowler.
Nagging length around off, Usman Khawaja goes on the back foot and nudges it down with soft hands past the first slip.
Full and around off, caressed through extra cover for an easy single.
A bit more round-arm, trying to angle it in from outside off, Cameron Green stays solid in defense.
Floated up outside off, this is firmly driven to short extra cover.
Very full and around off, punched on the up down to long off for a single.
Tossed up, full and on leg, Cameron Green tucks it towards short mid-wicket.

OUT! CAUGHT BEHIND! Ravichandran Ashwin strikes and India finally breaks this huge stand. A wicket against the run of play. Ashwin bowls this flatter and down the leg, Cameron Green goes down to sweep it away, but goes through the shot a bit early as the ball arrives late and brushes against his gloves towards the keeper where Srikar Bharat takes a sharp low catch moving to his right. They appeal for it, and up goes the finger. Cameron Green walks back after a fine innings.
Howout: c Srikar Bharat b Ravichandran Ashwin

Commentary: Floated, full and on middle, Alex Carey defends it back to the bowler.
Flighted, full and on middle, Alex Carey drives it towards mid on.
Looped up, full and on off, Alex Carey strides forward and knocks it towards covers.

OUT! TAKEN! Ravichandran Ashwin with the double whammy! Alex Carey tries to take on Ashwin, but holes out instead for a duck. This is flighted, full and well outside off, Alex Carey fails to control the temptation and goes for the slog-sweep against the turn, but slices it up in the air and Axar Patel at short third man takes a comfortable catch. Australia six down now!
Howout: c Axar Patel b Ravichandran Ashwin

Commentary: Flatter, full and on leg, Usman Khawaja stays there and paddles it towards fine leg for a single.
Tossed up, full and on off, Mitchell Starc drives it through covers for a couple of runs as Umesh Yadav chases and dives to keep it inside.
Flighted, full and on off, Mitchell Starc keeps it out to the off side.
Quicker, full and on off, Mitchell Starc steers it towards point for a single.
A bit short and on off, Usman Khawaja moves across and blocks it out.
Short and outside off again, Usman Khawaja is solid in his defense again.
Full and on off, Mitchell Starc drives it towards mid off.
Back of a length and around leg, Mitchell Starc nudges it towards fine leg for a single.
Fuller one and on leg, Usman Khawaja flicks it towards fine leg for a run.
This is on a good length and outside off, Mitchell Starc tries to push it away, but misses it completely.
BEATEN! Mohammad Shami bowls this on a hard length and on off, nips away a bit, Mitchell Starc gets beaten on the outside edge as he looks to fend it away.
Touch fuller and on off, shaping in, Mitchell Starc knocks it to the right of the bowler.
Tossed up, full and on off, Usman Khawaja drives it through cover-point for a single.
Floated, full and on off, Mitchell Starc pushes it towards short covers.
Looped up, full and on off, Mitchell Starc waits for it and keeps it out to the off side.
Flighted, full and on middle, Mitchell Starc turns it towards short mid-wicket.
Gives this one some air as well, on middle, Mitchell Starc leans on and blocks it out.
Shorter in length and outside off, turning in, Mitchell Starc moves back and cuts it towards sweeper covers for a run.
Fuller in length and outside off, Mitchell Starc shoulders arms to it.
Full again and on off, Mitchell Starc tries to drive on the up, but gets beaten on the outside edge.
This is on a good length and around off, angling in, Mitchell Starc plays inside the line and misses it.
Pitched up, on leg, angling in, Mitchell Starc flicks it through mid-wicket for a single.
BEAUTY! Mohammad Shami lands this on a hard length and on off, Usman Khawaja looks to fend it away, but gets beaten by the pace and misses as he is late into the shot.
On a length again and on the sixth stump line, Usman Khawaja thinsk about dabbing it away, but withdraws his bat at the last moment. End of a testing over!
Floated, full and on leg, Mitchell Starc turns it towards short mid-wicket.
Short and on middle, Mitchell Starc moves back and knocks it towards the bowler.

OUT! TAKEN! Ravichandran Ashwin strikes again! He has been brilliant in this session and sends Mitchell Starc back to the hut now. He bowls this slower through the air, on middle, tempting the batter to come on the front foot, Mitchell Starc obliges and tries to fend it, but gets an uppish inside edge and Shreyas Iyer at short leg shows good reflexes and takes a fine low catch. Australia lose their seventh wicket!
Howout: c Shreyas Iyer b Ravichandran Ashwin

Commentary: Tossed up, full and on off, Nathan Lyon blocks it out.
Flighted, full and on off, Nathan Lyon drives it towards point.
Another wicket-maiden from Ashwin! This is floated, full and on off, Nathan Lyon defends it back to the bowler.
Full and on off, Usman Khawaja pushes it towards covers.

FOUR! Easy pickings for Usman Khawaja! Mohammad Shami serves this full and on the pads, Usman Khawaja tickles it wide of the keeper where Srikar Bharat dives to his right, but fails to reach it and the ball races to the fin leg fence for a boundary.
On a length and on middle, Usman Khawaja taps it back to the bowler.
Touch fuller and off, Usman Khawaja drives it towards covers for a single.
Full again and on middle, Nathan Lyon negotiates it well.
This is pitched up, on off, Nathan Lyon drives it towards covers.
Tossed up, full and on off, turning away, Usman Khawaja leaves it alone.
Floated, full and on middle, angling in, Usman Khawaja stays back and keeps it out to the leg side.
Shortish and on middle, Usman Khawaja flicks it off the back foot towards mid on for a single.
Flighted, full and on middle, Nathan Lyon prods forward and blocks it out.
Slower through the air, on middle, Nathan Lyon knocks it back to bowler.
Looped up, full and on off, Nathan Lyon is solid in his defense again.
Overpitched and on off, Usman Khawaja drives it straight to covers.
On a length and on off, Usman Khawaja guides it through point for a single.
Length again and on off, Nathan Lyon chops it in front of first slip.
Touch fuller and on off, Nathan Lyon defends it back to the bowler.

EDGED AND FOUR! Umesh Yadav lands this on a good length and on off, angling in, Nathan Lyon looks to play at it, but gets an outside edge. However, it goes between the keeper and first slip for a boundary.
Fuller one and on middle, Nathan Lyon drills it towards mid on.
Tossed up, full and on off, Usman Khawaja stays back and knocks it wide of short covers.
Floated, full and on middle, Usman Khawaja defends it on the front foot.
Quicker, on middle, keeps low, Usman Khawaja stays there and does to well to keep it out.
Flighted, full and no off, Usman Khawaja drives it towards covers.
A bit short and on leg, Usman Khawaja tucks it towards short mid-wicket.
A maiden over! Ravichandran Ashwin floats this up outside off, Usman Khawaja offers no shot at it.
LEG BYE! This is very full and attacking the pads, Nathan Lyon looks to flick but misses. The ball goes off the pads toward backward square leg and they get a leg bye.
Good length, angling in from outside off, Usman Khawaja pushes it gently onto the off side.

Back of a length around off, Usman Khawaja flicks it off the back foot to the right of short mid-wicket. The fielder there dives and parries the ball toward mid off and the batters are able to scamper through for one. The 400 is now up for Australia.
This is pitched up on off stump, Lyon blocks it out.
Fullish length on middle, this is pushed gently to mid on.
Full and straight, played on the up toward mid off.
Short and around off, this is eased off the back foot by Usman Khawaja to deep cover-point for a single.
Flighted, around off, Nathan Lyon presses forward and edges it down with soft hands toward gully.
Gives it a lot of air and floats it up around off, Nathan Lyon blocks off the front foot.
This is quicker and around off, kept out by Lyon.
Comes from around the wicket and floats it up in the blockhole on middle and leg, Nathan Lyon manages to get some bat on it.
Around off stump, this is eased away toward cover.
Full and well outside off, Usman Khawaja reaches out and drives it to deep cover for a run.
On a length and outside off, Nathan Lyon bunts it off the bottom edgge toward first slip.
A bit fuller and on the fifth stump line, left alone by Nathan Lyon.
Short of a length outside off, Lyon wiats on the back foot and plays it with an angled bat toward deep backward point for one.
A bit fuller and angled in from well outside off, Usman Khawaja gets on the front foot and punches it toward sweeper cover for another single.
On a length and outside off, this is patted away toward cover.
Nice bit of flight and drift into the off stump, Usman Khawaja pushes it past silly point.
Tossed up full and on off stump, Usman Khawaja drives it a bit uppishly and through the cover region for a single.
Flighted once again, on middle and Nathan Lyon keeps it out.
Tosses it up now outside off, inviting the drive. Lyon mistimes the cover drive toward cover-point.
A bit flatter and on middle, Nathan Lyon gets behind the line and keeps it out.
Around off stump, Lyon leans forward to defend.
Goes wide of the crease and serves a good-length delivery around the top of off stump, Usman Khawaja keeps it out toward point.
Length again around off, this is played down with soft hands toward third man for a single.
Back of a length outside off, Nathan Lyon bends his back a bit and taps it toward cover.
Here comes the bumper now, this is bowled over off stump and at a good height as well. Nathan Lyon looks to hook it away but takes his eyes off the ball and misses.
On a length around off, pushed away to mid off.
Banged in short again around off, Nathan Lyon looks to pull but seems to have missed it. The ball goes off the back of the helmet and toward the man at fly slip.
Shorter one, a bit slower and around middle, this is worked away off the back foot in front of square leg for one.
On the pads, worked away toward mid-wicket for a single.
Nagging length around off, Usman Khawaja hangs back and pokes at it late, keeping it down past the slip cordon.
Good running! Nicely flighted, full and around off, turning it away a touch. Usman Khawaja strokes it away toward backward point and gets across to the other end.
Floated up on a length and turning it in from outside off, Nathan Lyon pushes it on the off side.
Tossed up on the off stump, Nathan Lyon keeps it out. That will be Tea on Day 2!

OUT! LBW! A lazy prod right after the break from Usman Khawaja and all the hard work is undone in a jiffy. Axar Patel starts off with a shortish delivery on middle and leg, turning it in. Khawaja goes on the back foot and casually looks to flick it away but misses and gets pinged on the pads. There is a huge shout for LBW but it is turned down. After a bit of discussion, the stand in skipper Cheteshwar Pujara takes the review. UltraEdge is checked first and there's no bat involved. Ball Tracking comes up with three reds and Khawaja has to walk back after a mamoth knock.
Full and outside off, Todd Murphy reaches out and eases it toward cover-point.
Flatter one on off stump, blocked off the front foot.
Flights it up now on off stump, Todd Murphy leans forward to defend.
Flatter one, angling across off, kept out by Murphy.
A wicket-maiden! Flatter and around off, Todd Murphy defends it out.
Starts off with a flatter delivery on middle and off, Nathan Lyon makes the block.
Flights this one across the right-hander, Lyon eases it on the off side.
Around off stump, blocked out.
Full and on middle, Nathan Lyon jams it out to mid on.
This is shorter and angling well across the off stump, Nathan Lyon looks to poke at it but misses.
BEATEN! Nicely flighted once again, on a nagging length and around off, Lyon looks to push at it but ghets beaten on the outside edge.
Very full and on the pads, this is flicked away toward fine leg for a couple of runs.
Tossed up on leg stump, Todd Murphy defends it out.
This one is angled across the left-hander, Todd Murphy strides forward and pushes it through the point region for a quick single.
Floated up on the leg stump line, Nathan Lyon defends it with soft hands.
Gives it a bit more air and bowls it around middle, Lyon makes the block.
Close! Axar Patel bowls it quicker and tries angling it in from outside off. Nathan Lyon looks to drive but misjudges the length and is beaten on the inside edge.
Short and around off, cut away behind backward point for a quick single.
Shorter one, angled well across the off stump, Nathan Lyon stands tall and punches it toward mid off.

Nicely tossed up on the pads, Nathan Lyon looks for the sweep but seems to have missed it and gets hit on the pads. There is an appeal for LBW but it is turned down. No review is taken either and that's a good decision as the replays show that there was glove involved.
Tossed up full and on middle, Lyon drives it straight back but Ravichandran Ashwin makes a good diving stop to his right.
Floated up around off, blocked out.
FOUR! One of those that slips out of the hand. This is way too short and wide, Nathan Lyon rocks back and cuts it hard into the vacant cover-point fence.

FOUR! Good shot! This is flatter and short, outsdie off, Todd Murphy punches it towards point where Ravindra Jadeja starts to move to his left and is late to change direction and the ball races towards the deep point fence for a boundary.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Todd Murphy blocks it back to the bowler.
On off, kept out.
Quciker, full and on off, Todd Murphy defends it on the front foot.
This one keeps very low, on middle, Todd Murphy stays back and does to well to tuck it away through square leg for a single.
Flighted, full and on middle, Nathan Lyon pushes it back to the bowler.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Todd Murphy leans on and blocks it out.
Floated, full and on middle, Todd Murphy defends it with the inner half past short leg.
Flighted, full and on middle, Todd Murphy keeps it out down the pitch.
Flatter, full and on leg, Todd Murphy is solid in his defense again.
Shortish and around off, Todd Murphy moves back and cuts it towards point.
Looped up, full and on middle, Todd Murphy knocks it back to the bowler.
Angles this one into the batter, on leg, Nathan Lyon blocks it back to the bowler.
Darts this one full and on leg, keeps low, Nathan Lyon looks to flick it, but misses and gets hit on the pads.

Uppish but safe! This is tossed up, full and on middle, Nathan Lyon drives it uppishly back towards the bowler where Axar Patel dives to his right, but fails to grab it. A good attempt though. A single is also taken.
Floated, full and on middle, Todd Murphy blocks it out.
Slower through the air, on off, Todd Murphy looks to defend it with soft hands and gets an outside edge along the ground wide of slip for a couple of runs.
FOUR! Nice shot! This is short and outside off, Todd Murphy frees his arms and cuts it through cover-point for a boundary.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Nathan Lyon keeps it out to the leg side.
On middle, blocked out.
A bit short and on off, Nathan Lyon moves back and defends it onto the pitch.
Flighted and around middle, Nathan Lyon goes down and tries to sweep it away, but misses and gets his around his forearm. There is a stiffled appeal for LBW, but turned down.
Flatter, full and down the leg, Nathan Lyon misses his flick and Srikar Bharat does well to collect it behind the stumps moving to his left.
Fires this one full and down the leg, Nathan Lyon looks to clip it, but misses.
Mohammad Shami steams in and bangs in a bouncer, on middle, Todd Murphy gets hurried and awkwardly ducks under it. However, he has overstepped and it is a No Ball.
Fuller one and on middle, angling in, Todd Murphy pushes it towards covers.
Full again and on off, Todd Murphy opens the face of the bat and guides it towards deep point for a single.
Overpitched and outside off, Nathan Lyon reaches out for it and drills it towards deep point for a run.
FOUR! Just wide! Mohammad Shami serves this full again and on off, Todd Murphy goes for the drive on the up, but gets an outside edge well past the diving second slip for a boundary.
Mohammad Shami lands this short but down the leg side, Todd Murphy tries to hook it away, but misses.
On a length and on middle, angling in, Todd Murphy gets cramped and misses his flick to get hit high on his pads.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Nathan Lyon drills it back to the bowler.
Floated, full and on middle, Nathan Lyon eases it towards long on for a single.
Flighted, full and on off, Todd Murphy drives it past the diving cover fielder for a brace.
Slower through the air, on off, turning away, Todd Murphy steers it towards point.
Fires a yorker now, on off, Todd Murphy squeezes it towards point again.
A bit short and on middle, Todd Murphy moves back and flicks it towards square leg. Lyon wants the run, but he is sent back.
Full and outside off, shaping away, Nathan Lyon throws his bat at it, but fails to connect.
FOUR! Fine shot! Mohammad Shami bangs this short and on middle, Nathan Lyon is already waiting for it and pulls it towards the vacant deep mid-wicket fence for a boundary.
