Goes fuller and on middle, Nathan Lyon drives it wide of mid on.
On a length and on off, Nathan Lyon dabs it through cover-point for a single.

MISFIELD AND FOUR! Mohammad Shami bowls a full toss, outside off, Todd Murphy thrashes it towards the deep point fence where Ravichandran Ashwin runs from third man and reaches it, but a tired effort from him lets it through for a boundary.
Short of a length and on middle, angling in, Todd Murphy taps it down towards square leg for a run.
Tossed up, full and on off, turning in, Todd Murphy cuts it towards backward point.
Short and outside off, Todd Murphy looks to cut it again, but misses this time.
Short again and outside off, Todd Murphy connects this time with his cut shot towards deep point for a single. 450 up for Australia!
Quicker, full and on leg, Nathan Lyon clips it wide of deep square leg for a couple of runs.
Floated, short and on leg, Nathan Lyon looks to flick, but misses as the ball loops up off his pads towards short leg where Shreyas Iyer pouches it. There is an appeal for the catch, but turned down.
Short again and on leg, Nathan Lyon moves back and flicks it uppishly towards short leg, but it falls just short of Shreyas Iyer.
Tossed up, full and on leg, Todd Murphy turns it towards short mid-wicket.
Short and on middle, Todd Murphy stays back and keeps it out down the pitch.
FOUR! Fine shot! This is floated, full and around leg, Todd Murphy goes down and nails his sweep shot towards the deep square leg fence for a boundary.
Flighted, full and on middle, Todd Murphy knocks it back to the bowler.

Brilliant fielding in the deep! This is looped up, full and on middle, Todd Murphy paddles it towards the vacant fine leg region, Umesh Yadav runs from deep square leg and puts in a dive to his left to stop it. Two runs taken!
Shortish and on off, Todd Murphy defends it on the back foot.
Tossed up, full and on off, Nathan Lyon keeps it out to the off side.
Floated, full and on middle, Nathan Lyon leans on to block it out.
A bit short and on middle, Nathan Lyon is solid in his defense again.
Flighted, full and on middle, Nathan Lyon prods forward to defend again.
On off, kept out.
A maiden over! This is flatter, full and on middle, Nathan Lyon drills it back towards the bowler.
This is bowled flatter and around off, Todd Murphy blocks it out.
Quicker one angling across off, Todd Murphy goes on the back foot and cuts it late down to third man for one. The 50-run stand is up between these two, a vital stand for Australia.
Flighted delivery, on a length and on middle, Lyon keeps it out.
Fuller and on middle, kept out.
This is full again and angled into middle and leg, Nathan Lyon blocks it off the front foot.
This is floated up on the stumps, Lyon makes yet another solid block.
Tossed up full and outside off, inviting the drive. Todd Murphy drives it past the fielder at short cover and picks up a single.
On off stump, Nathan Lyon looks to push at it but gets an inside edge that goes past square leg. They pick up one.
Looped up now around off, Murphy pushes it toward cover.
Nicely tossed up, full and around off, this is driven off the outer half of the bat behind backward point for one more.
Flighted one on middle, blocked out.
Flatter and on off stump, Nathan Lyon eases it toward mid off.

LEG BYE! Tossed up around the leg stump, Todd Murphy misses the sweep and the ball goes off the pads behind square leg. There is an appeal for lbw but it is turned down and the batters pick up a leg bye.
A tad shorter around off, cut away to backward point.
Pushed through on off stump, blocked.
Around off again and Lyon makes another block.
This is darted in on off stump, Nathan Lyon defends it out.
A bit slower and angling into middle and off, Lyon keeps it out.
This is flatter and on off stump, Todd Murphy blocks it out.
Another one pushed through on off stump, Murphy defends it off the front foot.
Slows it up and bowls it shorter around middle and leg, Todd Murphy looks to work it leg side but fails to do so.
At the stumps, blocked out.
Comes from over the wicket now and angles it in from around off, kept out.
Floated up outside off, Todd Murphy caresses it through the point region for a single.

Starts off with a full and wide one, Todd Murphy latches onto it and hammers it in front of point. Ravichandran Ashwin sprints to his left from deep backward point and cuts it off, keeping it down to a couple of runs.
Good length around off, this is guided through backward point for a single.
FOUR! This pair is really making a big difference out there. This is pitched up on off stump, Nathan Lyon clears the front leg and lofts it right back over the bowler's head for a boundary.
FOUR! Another boundary! Banged in short and at the body, Nathan Lyon instinctively swivel-pulls it firmly and into the backward square leg fence.
On a length just angling down leg, Lyon looks to get a tickle on it but misses.

FOUR! Adding insult to injury and 15 runs come off the first over with the new ball. This is bowled full and outside off, Nathan Lyon looks to drive but gets an inside edge past the stumps and the ball runs away into the fine leg fence.
Tossed up full and outside off, driven straight to short cover.
On off stump, kept out by Todd Murphy.

OUT! LBW! This is bowled flatter and angled in from middle, staying low as well. Todd Murphy looks to push at it but leaves a huge gap between bat and pad and misses the block. The ball hits him on the pads and there is a big appeal. The finger goes up and Ravichandran Ashwin has done the trick once again it seems but Todd Murphy has reviewed it. Nothing on UltraEdge and Ball Tracking shows that it is just clipping leg stump which means the on-field decision stands and Ashwin gets yet another five-fer in Test cricket, excellent from him. Murphy departs but he played a fine knock.
Full and outside off, pushed out toward cover.
Tosses it up nicely around off and this one grips and turns away nicely. Matthew Kuhnemann looks to block but is well beaten.
And again! Slower through the air and floated up around off, turning away and beats the outside edge yet again.
Flatter one on the stumps, blocked out.
Shorter in length and around off, pushed away through cover-point for a single.
Flatter one around off, kept out on the off side.
Full on middle and leg, pushed back to the bowler.
Quicker one, sliding it across the off stump, Matthew Kuhnemann looks to play at it but is well beaten.
Shorter and around off, kept out by Matthew Kuhnemann.
Quicker one, fired in full and down the leg side, Nathan Lyon looks to flick but misses.

OUT! TAKEN! Ravichandran Ashwin picks up his sixth wicket of the innings and Australia have been finally bundled out. Nicely flighted on a length and around off stump, Nathan Lyon puts a big stride forward as he looks to block. Lyon though doesn't get to the pitch of the ball and the outside edge is found. The ball flicks the keeper's legs and loops up kindly to Virat Kohli at first slip and he makes no mistake. Lyon's solid resistance comes to an end and Australia finish with 480 runs on the board.
Howout: c Virat Kohli b Ravichandran Ashwin

Commentary: LEG BYE! A big appeal for lbw on the very first delivery but it is turned down and they don't review it. Starts off with a length ball around the leg stump and just swinging it back in a touch. Rohit Sharma looks to flick it away but misses. The ball goes off the pads down to fine leg and they get a leg bye.
On a good length and on the pads, Shubman Gill works it down to fine leg to get off the mark with a single.
FOUR! Sweetly timed and Rohit Sharma is off the mark in style! A bit too full and straight from Mitchell Starc and Rohit just times it through the mid-wicket region for a boundary.
Good-length delivery, at 145.3 clicks and angling well across the right-hander. Rohit Sharma leaves it alone.
Length ball right on the money at over 143 clicks and Rohit blocks it out.
Excellent running! Pitches this one up around off, Rohit Sharma blocks it off the front foot in front of extra cover and scampers through to the other end.
Starts off with a good-length delivery on leg stump, Rohit Sharma gets inside the line and works it 'round the corner for a single.
FOUR! Glorious from Shubman Gill! Back of a length outside off, Gill plays a back-foot jab and times it to perfection. The ball rockets into the point fence.
Around the hips, this is tucked away behind square on the leg side for a single.
This is shorter and outside off, Rohit Sharma stands tall and taps it to deep point for one more.
Perfect length, swinging it in from outside off, Shubman Gill looks to block off the front foot but gets an inside edge onto the leg side.
Pitches this one up on middle and leg, Gill drives it to the right of mid on.
On a length and on middle, Rohit Sharma turns it to the right of short mid-wicket.
Touch fuller and on middle, Rohit Sharma keeps it out to the leg side.
This is on a hard length and on middle, Rohit Sharma looks to flick it away, but misses and gets hit on the pads as the ball rolls towards point.
Mitchell Starc strays away from his line and serves this full, but down the leg, Rohit Sharma misses his flick and Alex Carey gathers it behind the stumps.
Fuller one and on middle, Rohit Sharma tucks it towards short mid-wicket.
Pulls his length back a bit, on off, Rohit Sharma pushes it towards short covers.
Back of a length and around off, Shubman Gill punches it wide of deep point for a brace.
This is on a good length and on middle, Shubman Gill blocks it out to the bowler.
Goes fuller and on off, Shubman Gill leans on and defends it towards short covers.
This is pitched up and on off, Shubman Gill leans into his drive and times it well though covers as Travis Head chases it down and slides to keep it inside. Two runs taken!
Fullish and on middle, Shubman Gill knocks it towards mid off.
On a length and on off, Shubman Gill keeps it out towards mid off.
Fuller one and on off, Rohit Sharma pushes it towards mid off.
Full again and on off, Rohit Sharma mistimes his drive towards mid off.
Overpitched and outside off, Rohit Sharma absolutely smashes it, but straight to deep point. They cross.
This is pitched-up, on middle, Shubman Gill knocks it towards mid off.
Back of a length and on middle, Shubman Gill pucnhes it towards mid on.
Mitchell Starc lands this on a hard length and outside off, angling away, Shubman Gill leaves it alone.
Nathan Lyon starts with a floated delivery, short and on off, Rohit Sharma plays for the turn, but this keeps straight and misses the bat.
FOUR! In the gap! This is short and on off, Rohit Sharma slices it uppishly, but it goes well past backward point for a boundary.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Rohit Sharma blocks it out.
Flighted, full and on off, Rohit Sharma looks fend it, but gets an outside edge along the ground as Steven Smith at first slip dives to his right to stop it.
Looped up, full and on off, Rohit Sharma defends it on the front foot.
A bit short and on middle, Rohit Sharma moves back and nudges it towards deep square leg for a single.
Matthew Kuhnemann begins with a short delivery, on middle, Rohit Sharma moves back and flicks it, but it deflects off the short leg fiedler towards mid-wicket.
Tossed up, full and on off, Rohit Sharma drives it towards mid off for a single.
Floated and on middle, keeps low, Shubman Gill stays back and puts his bat down in time to keep it out.
Flighted, full and on middle, Shubman Gill blocks it down the pitch.
Looped up, full and on leg, Shubman Gill drills it towards mid on.
Flatter, full and on middle, Shubman Gill tucks it towards short mid-wicket.
Floated, full and on off, Rohit Sharma prods forward and blocks it out.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Rohit Sharma defends it back to the bowler.
Flighted, full and on off, Rohit Sharma pushes it towards short covers.
Gives this one some air, on off, Rohit Sharma uses his feet and eases it towards long on for a single.
Flatter, full and on middle, Shubman Gill leans on and keeps it out.
Shorter in length and on off, Shubman Gill moves back and punches it towards covers.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Rohit Sharma blocks it back to the bowler.
Shortish and on off, Rohit Sharma punches it towards sweeper covers for single.
Flighted, full and on middle, Shubman Gill drives it towards mid on.
Quicker, short and on middle, Shubman Gill stays there and pushes it towards short covers.
Darts this one full and on leg, Shubman Gill clips it wide of mid on for a run.
Gives this one some air, on off, Rohit Sharma negotiates it well.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Shubman Gill defends it back to the bowler.
SIX! Nice use of the feet! This is floated and on middle, Shubman Gill skips down the track and smokes it over the long on fence for a biggie.
Shortish and on middle, Shubman Gill moves back and nudges it through square leg for a single.
Flighted, full and on middle, Rohit Sharma is solid in his defense.
Looped up, full and on off, Rohit Sharma taps it with soft hand towards the short cover region for a run.
Floated, full and on middle, Shubman Gill prods forward and defends it back to the bowler. THAT WILL BE STUMPS ON DAY  2!
Mitchell Starc starts with a full delivery on the pads, Rohit Sharma tickles it towards fine leg for an easy single.
This is on a good length and outside off, Shubman Gill lets it go to the keeper.
Length again and on middle, Shubman Gill clips it towards mid on.
Goes fuller this time, on middle, angling in, Shubman Gill knocks it towards mid off.
A half-volley, on the leg stump line, Shubman Gill tucks it towards deep mid-wicket for a run.
Fullish and on middle, Rohit Sharma covers his stumps and keeps it out towards mid on.
Nathan Lyon begins with a flatter delivery, full and around off, Shubman Gill steers it towards point.
Tossed up, full and on off, Shubman Gill prods forward and blocks it down the pitch.
Floated, full and outside off, Shubman Gill keeps it out to the off side.
A bit short and on middle, Shubman Gill moves back and turns it towards short mid-wicket.
Quicker, full and on off, Shubman Gill leans on and defends it towards short covers.
A maiden over for Lyon! This is flighted and around off, turning in, Shubman Gill tries to defend it on the front foot, but gets an inside edge wide of short leg.
Full and on the pads again, Rohit Sharma flicks it towards deep square leg for a single.
FOUR! Nice shot! Mitchell Starc serves ths full and around off, Shubman Gill stays there and shows the full face of the bat to drive it firmly through covers for the firsr boundary of the Day.
Pulls his length back a bit, on middle and leg, Shubman Gill whips it wide of deep square leg and comes back for the second.
Back of a length and around off, Shubman Gill mistimes his cut towards short covers.

FOUR! Just wide! Mitchell Starc lands this short and down the leg side, Shubman Gill goes for the pull shot, but gloves it uppishly behind the stumps. However, it goes well wide of the diving keeper and towards the fine leg fence for a boundary.

Short of a length and on off, Shubman Gill makes room and awkwardly punches it towards the vacant long off region as the fielder from mid off chase it and dives forward to keep it in. Three runs taken!
Shortsh and around off, Shubman Gill stays there and blocks it down the pitch.
Tossed up, full and on off, Shubman Gill leans on and defends it in front of point.
Quicker, short and on middle, Shubman Gill moves back to flick it, but gets an inside edge onot his pads and the ball loops wide of short leg. They cross.
Floated, full and on off, Rohit Sharma defends it on the front foot.
Flatter, full and outside off, Rohit Sharma goes down and paddles it towards deep backward square leg for a run.
Gives this one some air as well, on off, Shubman Gill is solid in his defense.
On a length and on leg, Rohit Sharma misses his flick and the ball goes off his pads towards the keeper.
Length again and on off, Rohit Sharma pushes it towards mid off, and calls for the run, but refuses in the end.
Mitchell Starc lands this short and on leg, Rohit Sharma goes for the pull shot, but it is not that short and miscues his pull shot uppsishly towards backward sqaure leg.
FOUR! Easy pickings! This is short of a length and down the leg, Rohit Sharma stays there and helps it towards the fine leg fence for a boundary.
Back of a length and around off, Rohit Sharma stands tall and keeps it out to the off side.
SIX! BANG! Vintage Rohit Sharma! Mitchell Starc bangs this short again and around leg, sits up nicely, Rohit Sharma swivels and pulls it over the deep backward square leg fence for a biggie.
Tossed up, full and on off, turning in sharply, Shubman Gill leans on to defend, but misses and gets hit on he pads.
Slightly shorter in length and outside off, Shubman Gill goes on his back foot and defends it on the pitch.
Floated, full and on off, Shubman Gill keeps it out to the off side.
Flatter, full and on off, Shubman Gill pushes it towards mid off.
Shotish and on middle, Shubman Gill moves back and negotiates it well.
Another short delivery, on middle, Shubman Gill flicks it off the back foot through square leg for a single.
Matthew Kuhnemann starts with a floated delivery, full and on middle, Shubman Gill defends it with the inner half to the leg side.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Shubman Gill blocks it back to the bowler.
Flighted, full and on leg, Shubman Gill turns it towards short mid-wicket.
Flatter, full and on off, Shubman Gill drives it towards long off for a single.
Looped up, full and on middle, Rohit Sharma knocks it to the left of the bowler as Matthew Kuhnemann mops it up.
Gives this one some air as well, on middle, Rohit Sharma eases it towards long off for a run.
Tossed up and outside off, Rohit Sharma uses his feet and clips it towards long on for a single.
Floated and on middle, Shubman Gill comes forward and drills it towards the bowler as Nathan Lyon catches it. He fakes a celebration, but knows that it is a bump ball.

An appeal for LBW, but turned down. Australia takes the review after some discussion. Lyon bowls this quicker and on middle, Shubman Gill skips down the track to defend again, but his pad is in front of the bat and the ball hits it. UltraEdge confirms pad first, and Ball Tracking shows that the impact is outside off and also over 3 meters. So, the on-field decision of Not Out remains and Australia lose their review.
Fligthed, full and on off, Shubman Gill once again use his feet and blocks it with the inner half past short leg.
Short and outside off, Shubman Gill moves back and punches it towards deep point for a brace.
Quicker and on middle, Shubman Gill advances down the track and turns it to the leg side.
Floated, full and on middle, Rohit Sharma knocks it back to the bowler.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Rohit Sharma blocks it out.
Slower through the air, on off, Rohit Sharma taps it wide of short covers and scampers across for a single.
Flighted, full and on leg, Shubman Gill tucks it towards short mid-wicket.
Flatter, full and on middle, Shubman Gill keeps it out towards the short leg region.
Angles this one into the batter, short and on middle, Shubman Gill works it towards mid-wicket.
Tossed up, full and on off, Rohit Sharma guides it towards point.
Floated, full and on off, turning in, Rohit Sharma leans on to defend, but gets an inside edge onto his pads as the ball goes nowhere.
Darts this one full and on middle, Rohit Sharma drills it back to the bowler.
Flighted and around off, Rohit Sharma uses his feet and tucks it wide of mid-wicket for a single.
Shorter in length and on middle, Shubman Gill defends it on the back foot.
Quicker delivery, short and on off, Shubman Gill stays there and keeps it out on the pitch.
Matthew Kuhnemann floats this one full and on a leg stump line. Rohit Sharma blocks this back down the pitch.
Flights this one full and just outside the off stump. Rohit Sharma gets forward and dabs this towards cover.
Fires this one on a shortish length and into the pads. Rohit Sharma clips this towards deep square leg for an easy single.
Tosses this one really full and in line with the stumps. Shubman Gill flicks this towards the mid-wicket fielder.
Goes full once again and on off stump. Shubman Gill eases this down to long off for a run.

OUT! CAUGHT! SOFT SOFT DISMISSAL! Rohit Sharma falls to a poor shot selection against the run of play and Matthew Kuhnemann draws first blood! This is short and outside the off stump. Rohit Sharma rocks onto his back foot and looks to punch this into the off side. The ball seems to get stuck in the wicket and the batter ends up hitting it uppishly straight into the hands of Marnus Labuschagne at cover. Australia looks absolutely ecstatic with this wicket as the Indian skipper takes the long walk back to the shed.
Howout: c Marnus Labuschagne b Matthew Kuhnemann

Commentary: Nathan Lyon bowls this full and outside the off. The ball turns back in sharply as Shubman Gill looks to defend. The ball takes a slight inside edge and hits the pads. A massive appeal from Nathan Lyon but the umpire remains unmoved and they opt not to review this.
Flights this one on a fullish length and outside the off stump. Shubman Gill goes back in the crease and blocks this out.
Loops this one full and outside the off pole. Shubman Gill gets well forward to defend this back down the pitch.
Tosses this one full as well and outside the off stump. Shubman Gill shuffles down the wicket and dabs this back into the pitch.
Continues to float the ball full and this time wider outside off. Shubman Gill works this down to long on for one.

BEATEN! Nathan Lyon floats this one full and outside the off stump. the ball skids through without turning as Cheteshwar Pujara looks to block down the wrong line. The ball skims past the outside edge and that was a lovely delivery.
Matthew Kuhnemann tosses this one full and going down leg. Shubman Gill clips this towards deep square leg and collects a run.
Goes full and in line with the stumps. Cheteshwar Pujara knocks this back towards the bowler.
Bowls this straight as well on a fuller length. Cheteshwar Pujara gets forward in defense and the ball goes off the inside edge towards the leg side.
Loops this one full and on a leg stump line. Cheteshwar Pujara dabs this to the right of the bowler.
Tosses this one full and at the stumps. Cheteshwar Pujara shimmies down the wicket and flicks the ball towards deep square leg to open his account with a couple of runs.

Flights this one full and outside the off stump. Cheteshwar Pujara gets a stride forward and looks to defend but gets beaten on the outside edge. The ball hits him on the back leg and goes into the off side. Matthew Kuhnemann appeals but Steven Smith decides to not go for the review.
Nathan Lyon bowls this full and outside off. Shubman Gill stays in the crease and dabs this into the leg side.
Fires this one full and into the stumps. Shubman Gill punches this down to long on and takes a single.
Floats this one wide outside off on a fuller length. Cheteshwar Pujara gets his front foot forward and pads the ball into the off side.
Tosses this one full and outside the off stump. Cheteshwar Pujara shuffles down the wicket and clips this towards deep mid-wicket for a run.
Flights this one full and outside the off pole. Shubman Gill gets his front foot forward confidently and blocks this out.
Slightly short this time and outside the off stump. Shubman Gill rocks back and punches this to the left of cover to take one and retain strike.
Matthew Kuhnemann bowls a full delivery on the pads. Shubman Gill dabs this into the leg side.
Tosses this one full and going down leg. Shubman Gill pushes this towards deep mid-wicket and takes one.
Edged and just short! Matthew Kuhnemann flights this full and outside off. Cheteshwar Pujara looks to defend and gets an outside egde thedgealls short of Steven Smith at first slip.
Bowls this one slightly quicker and onto the pads. Cheteshwar Pujara taps this towards short leg.
Loopy delivery bowled full and in line with the stumps. Cheteshwar Pujara uses his feet once again and flicks this towards deep square leg for a single.
NO BALL! Continues to bowl full and at the stumps. Shubman Gill blocks this back together. The over is not complete though as Matthew Kuhnemann has overstepped and it will be a no ball.
Floats this one full and on a leg stump line. Shubman Gill defends this solidly to the right of the bowler.
Nathan Lyon bowls this slightly short and outside the off stump. Cheteshwar Pujara uses his feet nicely and punches this towards deep cover for a couple of runs.
Tosses this one full and outside the off stump. Cheteshwar Pujara blocks this back towards trhe bowler.
Flights this one full and outside the off pole. Cheteshwar Pujara comes down the wicket and dabs this towards cover for a quick single.
Loopy delivery bowled full and outside off. Shubman Gill is weel forward as he taps this into the off side.
Bowls this one in line with the stumps on a fuller length. Shubman Gill plays this confidently back towards the bowler.
Goes back to bowling outside the off stump on a fuller length. Shubman Gill defends this solidly towards cover.
Strays onto the pads on a fuller length. Cheteshwar Pujara clips this to short fine leg and takes one.
Bowls this one slightly short and at the pads. Shubman Gill rocks back and flicks this towards deep backward square leg for a run.
Floats this one full and in line with the stumps. Cheteshwar Pujara plays this with soft hands towards fine leg and picks up a couple of runs.
Tosses this one full and just outside the off stump. Cheteshwar Pujara dabs this towards square leg.
Goes full once again and into the stumps. Cheteshwar Pujara uses his feet well once again to get to the pitch of the ball and flick it towards deep square leg for a single.
Bowls this one a tad bit short and on a leg-stump line. Shubman Gill tucks this to backward square leg and takes a run.
Nathan Lyon starts the over with a shortish delivery outside off. Shubman Gill goes deep in the crease and clips this towards deep mid-wicket for a single.
Floats this one full and outside the off stump. Cheteshwar Pujara shuffles forward and smothers the ball into the pitch.
Loopy delivery bowled full and outside off. Cheteshwar Pujara is down the wicket again and the ball lobs up off his pads towards the bowler.
Fires this one full and wide outside off. Cheteshwar Pujara gets his front foot forward and leaves the ball alone.
Flighted delivery bowled full and outside off. Cheteshwar Pujara shuffles outside off and looks to block but the ball hits the pad first.
Another tossed-up delivery outside off. Cheteshwar Pujara is down the wicket again and gets this off his pads towards mid on.
Mitchell Starc starts this spell from 'round the wicket and bowls this on a good length, outside off. Shubman Gill blocks this solidly towards mid on.

FOUR! That is FIFTY for Shubman Gill and he has looked really comfortable so far at the crease! This is bowled slightly back of a length and wider outside off. Shubman Gill stands tall and punches this towards deep cover for a cracking boundary to reach his landmark.
Continues to bowl on a good length and outside the off stump. Shubman Gill defends this firmly towards cover.
Goes full this time and outside the off pole. Shubman Gill gets his front foot into the drive and cracks this straight to the cover fielder.
Persists with the fuller length and just outside off. Shubman Gill knocks this to the left of mid on and sets off for a single.
This is bowled full and well outside the off stump. Cheteshwar Pujara guides this towards deep point and takes a run. Brings up the 100 for India as well and they are off to a good start here.
Nathan Lyon bowls this short and outside off. Cheteshwar Pujara comes forward initially and then rocks back to cut the ball towards point.
Tosses this one full and outside the off stump. Cheteshwar Pujara charges down the wicket and flicks the ball to deep square leg for a single.
Nathan Lyon goes 'round the wicket now and bowls this full, in line with the stumps. Shubman Gill blocks this back down the pitch.
Floats this one full as well and outside off. Shubman Gill gets well forward and defends this to the left of the bowler.
Delivers this one slightly short and outside the off stump. Shubman Gill goes deep in the crease and keeps the ball out.
Goes back to bowling over the wicket and serves this on a fuller length outside off. Shubman Gill continues to be solid in defense as he pushes this towards short cover.
Back of a length and on the leg stump line, Cheteshwar Pujara misses his flick and the ball goes off his body towards fine leg. A leg bye is taken.
This is on a good length and on off, Shubman Gill taps it towards covers.
Touch fuller, on middle, angling in, Shubman Gill knocks it towards mid on.
Overpitched and on middle, Shubman Gill drives it towards mid on again.
FOUR! Fine shot! Mitchell Starc lands this back of a length and on middle, Shubman Gill stays back and jabs it with an angled bat towards the deep mid-wicket fence for a boundary.
Short of a length and on off, Shubman Gill dabs it towards cover-point for a single.
Todd Murphy begins with a tossed up delivery, full and on off, Shubman Gill drives it towards covers for a single.
Floated, full and on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara pushes it to the right of the bowler.
Slower through the air, on off, Cheteshwar Pujara uses his feet to defend, but misses and it goes off the pads to the leg side.
Flighted, full and on off, Cheteshwar Pujara leans on and blocks it out.
Shortish and on off, Cheteshwar Pujara moves back and keeps it out to the off side.
Quicker, full and on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara negotiates it down the pitch.
Mitchell Starc bowls this on a yorker length and on middle, Shubman Gill digs it out well towards mid on for a quick single.
On a length and on off, Cheteshwar Pujara opens the face of his bat and guides through point for a run.

Oh..that is close! Mitchell Starc serves this touch fuller and on off, Shubman Gill tries to drive it away from the body, but gets an inside edge just past the stumps towards fine leg for another run.
Overpitched and on off, Cheteshwar Pujara drives it straight to mid off.

A lot happening in the middle! Mitchell Starc pitches it up again and on off, Cheteshwar Pujara drives it firmly through covers as Travis Head from mid off chase it and slides to just keep it inside. The batters take a couple of runs, but Gill wants the third as well. However, Cheteshwar Pujara sends him back and rightly so as Gill has to dive in to get home.
Full again and on off, Cheteshwar Pujara drills it towards short covers.
Flatter, full and on middle, Shubman Gill eases it towards long on for a single.
FOUR! Nice use of the feet! This is tossed up and on off, Cheteshwar Pujara advances down the track, gets to the pitch of the ball and smashes it through covers for a boundary.
Flighted, full and on off, Cheteshwar Pujara uses his feet and pushes it straight back to the bowler.
Pushed through quicker, short and on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara turns it to the leg side.
Slower through the air, on off, Cheteshwar Pujara watches it through and dabs it towards point.
Shortish and on off, Cheteshwar Pujara steers it towards point again.
Cameron Green starts with a good-length delivery around off, Shubman Gill opens the face of his bat and guides it through point and comes back for the second very easily.
Length again and on middle, Shubman Gill nudges it towards short mid-wicket.
Touch fuller and on off, Shubman Gill strides forward and pushes it towards mid off.
Pulls his length back a bit, on middle, Shubman Gill jabs it towards mid on.
Goes fuller this time, on middle, swinging in, Shubman Gill drives it towards mid off.
This is on a good length and on pff, Shubman Gill taps it wide of short covers as Steven Smith runs to his right to collect it.
Short and on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara moves back and flicks it towards deep square leg for a single.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Shubman Gill leans on and blocks it back to the bowler.

FOUR BYES! Wow..how did that miss? Todd Murphy floats this up, full and on off, turning in sharply, Shubman Gill prods forward to drive it but misses as the ball just goes over the stumps. Alex Carey fails to gather it as well and the ball races to the fine leg fence for four extra runs. Brings up the 50-run partnership between these two.
Flighted, full and on middle, Shubman Gill defends it on the front foot.
Shorter in length and on middle, turning in, Shubman Gill works it towards square leg for a run.
Flatter, full and on of, Cheteshwar Pujara keeps it out to the off side.
Ful and on off, Shubman Gill mistimes his drive towards short covers.
Short of a length and outside off, Shubman Gill cuts it towards deep point for a single.
Back of a length and outside off again, Cheteshwar Pujara lifts his bat and lets it go to the keeper.
Cameron Green bowls an inswinger, full and on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara clips it towards deep square leg for a run.
Short and on off, Shubman Gill jabs it powerfully towards deep mid-wicket for just a run.
On a length and on off, Cheteshwar Pujara taps it towards short covers. THAT WILL BE LUNCH ON DAY 3!
Shorter in length and on off, Shubman Gill moves back and nudges it through mid-wicket for a single.
Flatter, full and outside off, Cheteshwar Pujara takes his front leg out, but leaves it alone.
Shortish and on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara defends it of the back foot.
Floated and on off, Cheteshwar Pujara uses his feet and yorks himself, and then turns it towards short mid-wicket.
Slower through the air, on off, Cheteshwar Pujara waits for it and dabs it towards point.
Looped up, full and on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara uses his feet again and drills back to the bowler.
Full and on off, Shubman Gill pushes it towards short covers.
Fuller again, but this time on the pads, Shubman Gill clips it towards finel leg for a single.
This is pitched up and on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara tucks it towards mid on.
Overpitched and on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara flicks it through square leg for a run.
Another full delivery, on middle, Shubman Gill turns it towards short mid-wicket.
FOUR! Lovely shot! Cameron Green continues with his fuller length, on middle this time, Shubman Gill moves across a bit and times his drive sweetly wide of mid on for a boundary.
Short and on off, Cheteshwar Pujara moves back and dabs it towards point.

Floated, full and on off, Cheteshwar Pujara prods forward to defend, but the ball hits his pads first and rolls to the off side. There is a stiffled appeal for LBW, but turned down. Nathan Lyon is asking the umpire if Cheteshwar Pujara padded it deliberately or not, but the umpire gives no hint as the DRS timer was still on.
Tossed up, full and on off, Cheteshwar Pujara uses his feet and tucks it towards mid-wicket for a single.
Flatter, full and on off, Shubman Gill drills it back to the bowler.
Shortish and on middle, Shubman Gill flicks it towards short leg.
Quicker, full and on off, Shubman Gill knocks it towards short covers.

FOUR! Deft touch! Cameron Green lands this on a good length and around off, Cheteshwar Pujara waits for it and opens the face of his bat to guide it past the keeper and towards the third man fence for a boundary.
Goes fuller this time, on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara blocks it down the pitch.
This is pitched up, on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara tucks it wide of short mid-wicket where the fielder dives to his right to stop it.
On a length and on off, Cheteshwar Pujara pushes it towards short covers.
Overpitched and on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara works it towards mid on.
Back of a length and on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara hops up and keeps it down towards short mid-wkcket.
Nathan Lyon floats this one full and outside off. Shubman Gill blocks this back to the bowler.
Bowls this slower in the air and wide outside off on a fuller length. Shubman Gill goes back and knocks this towards mid on.
Tosses this one full and outside the off pole. Shubman Gill gets forward and pushes this towards cover.
Fires this one full and just outside the off stump. Shubman Gill defends this back towards the bowler.
Loopy delivery bowled full and outside off. Shubman Gill shimmies down the wicket and clips this towards the man at short mid on.
Bowls this one at the stumps on a fuller length. Shubman Gill flicks this towards deep square leg and takes a single to keep strike. Just one run from the over.
Cameron Green bowls this on a good length and angles this in from outside off. Shubman Gill gets behind the line of the ball and defends this to short mid on.
Goes a touch fuller and outside the off stump. Shubman Gill drives this towards mid on.
Bowls this full and into the pads with the wicket-keeper up to the stumps. Shubman Gill clips this towards deep square leg and takes a single.
On a good length this time and outside the off pole. Cheteshwar Pujara gets on his toes and dabs this into the off side.
Delivers this one a tad bit shot and into the batter. Cheteshwar Pujara gets well on top of the bounce and dabs this towards mid-wicket.
Goes back to bowling on a good length and outside the off stump. Cheteshwar Pujara blocks this solidly towards mid off.
Nathan Lyon floats this one full and outside the off stump. Shubman Gill gets across the stumps and tucks this towards mid-wicket.
Tosses this one full and outside the off stump. Shubman Gill pushes forward and knocks this back to the bowler.
Slightly short and spinning into the stumps. Shubman Gill goes deep in the crease and keeps the ball out.
Flights this one full and outside the off pole. Shubman Gill shimmies down the wicket and hits this firmly to the fielder at cover,
Loopy delivery bowled full and outside the off stump. Shubman Gill defends this to the left of the bowler.
A maiden over for Nathan Lyon. This is bowled full and just outside off. Shubman Gill gets his front foot to the pitch of the ball and blocks this back to the bowler.
Mitchell Starc starts from 'round the wicket and bowls this on a good length, into the stumps. Cheteshwar Pujara defends this firmly to the short mid on fielder.
Goes full this time and attacks the stumps. Cheteshwar Pujara dabs this towards the covers and looks for a run. He is sent back by Shubman Gill.
Delivers this one full as well and just outside the off stump. Cheteshwar Pujara knocks this towards mid off.
Strays onto the pads on a fuller length. Cheteshwar Pujara clips this towards deep backward square leg for an easy single.
Comes over the wicket now and bowls this full, outside the off stump. Shubman Gill strokes this straight to the fielder at cover.
Goes full and outside the off stump with a seven-two field. Shubman Gill goes for the drive nevertheless and finds the cover fielder once again.
Nathan Lyon bowls this full and just outside off from 'round the wicket. Cheteshwar Pujara defends this watchfully into the off side.
Bowls this outside leg on a shortish length. Cheteshwar Pujara pushes this towards backward square leg.
Attacks the pads on a fuller length. Cheteshwar Pujara dabs this towards mid-wicket.
Flights this one full and on an off-stump line. Cheteshwar Pujara blocks this towards point.
Tosses this one full as well and outside the off stump. Cheteshwar Pujara eases this to the right of mid off and sets off for a quick single.
Bowls this one a fraction short and outside the off stump. Shubman Gill goes deep in the crease and dabs this towards short leg.
Mitchell Starc angles this one down leg side on a good length. Cheteshwar Pujara looks to flick this fine but misses.
Mitchell Starc goes full and wide outside the off stump. Cheteshwar Pujara pushes this towards deep cover-point and takes a couple of runs.
On a good length and outside the off stump. Cheteshwar Pujara blocks this solidly towards cover.
Goes fuller this time but going way down leg. Cheteshwar Pujara opts to leave this one alone.
Goes back to bowling on a good length and outside the off stump. Cheteshwar Pujara defends this towards the point fielder.
Nails the yorker this time outside the off pole. Cheteshwar Pujara digs this out towards cover.
Nathan Lyon floats this one full and just outside off. Shubman Gill clips this towards mid-wicket.
Tosses this one full and outside the off stump. Shubman Gill gets forward and defends it to the bowler's left.
Slightly short this time and outside the off stump. Shubman Gill rocks back and dabs this towards point.
Goes back to bowling full and at the stumps. Shubman Gill knocks this to short mid on.
Flights this one full and outside the off pole. Shubman Gill gets a good stride forward and pushes this towards cover.
Loopy delivery bowled full and outside off. Shubman Gill shimmies down the wicket and taps this into the off side.
Mitchell Starc goes full and into the stumps on a fuller length. Cheteshwar Pujara blocks this back towards the bowler.
On a good length this time and angling down leg. Cheteshwar Pujara looks to glance this fine but is unable to get bat on the ball.
Goes really full this time and attacks the stumps. Cheteshwar Pujara is rock solid as he dabs this towards mid on.
Anges this into the pads on a fuller length. Cheteshwar Pujara clips this to deep square leg and takes a run.
Continues to bowl full and outside the off stump. Shubman Gill eases this to the right of mid off and takes another single.
Bowls this on a good length and into the pads. Cheteshwar Pujara looks to play this leg side but misses and the ball comes off his thigh pad.
Nathan Lyon bowls this short and outside the off stump. Shubman Gill gets across the stumps and clips this towards deep mid-wicket for a single.
That single brings up the 150 for India! Nathan Lyon floats this full and on leg stump. Cheteshwar Pujara pushes at this and gets an outside edge towards third man for one.
Tosses this one full and outside the off stump. Shubman Gill blocks this back towards the bowler.
Slightly short once again and outside off. Shubman Gill goes deep in the crease and knocks this towards short mid on.
Loopy delivery bowled full and outside the off pole. Shubman Gill shuffles down the wicket and defends this towards cover.
Angles this into the stumps on a fuller length. Shubman Gill eases this down to long on for a single and will be on strike in the next over.
Mitchell Starc goes full and just outside the off stump. Shubman Gill taps this towards mid-wicket.
Bowls this one on a good length and aimed for the off pole. Shubman Gill covers the line of the ball and defends this towards mid-wicket.
Goes back to bowling full and outside the off stump. Shubman Gill goes hard at the ball but finds the fielder at mid off.
This is on a good length and wide outside off. Shubman Gill reaches for it and knocks this towards short cover.
Delivers this just outside the off stump on a fuller length. Shubman Gill keeps his head still and blocks this towards mid off.
A maiden over from Mitchell Starc. This is well outside the off pole on a fuller length. Shubman Gill leaves this one alone and Alex Carey dives to his right to collect the ball.
Tossed up, on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara uses his feet and forces it towards mid off.
A bit short and on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara moves back and keeps it out to the leg side.
Floated, full and on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara gets to the pitch of the ball and tucks it towards short mid-wicket.
Flighted, full and on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara uses his feet again and works it towards square leg.
Shortish and on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara nudges it wide of square leg.
A maiden over! This is looped up, full and on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara turns it towards short mid-wicket. Australia are trying to put pressure here!
Back of a length and on off, Shubman Gill dabs it down towards point.
Fullish and on the leg stump line, Shubman Gill clips it past the diving short mid-wicket fielder for a single.

This is pitched up and on leg again, Cheteshwar Pujara misses his flick and Alex Carey behind the stumps dives to his left to collect it. There is a leg slip for Pujara and this could have been close.
Full again and on the pads, Cheteshwar Pujara flicks it towards deep square leg for one.
Another full delivery, on middle, keeps low too, Shubman Gill manages to keep it out towards short mid-wicket.
On a length and on middle, Shubman Gill punches it towards mid on.
Floated, full and on off, Cheteshwar Pujara keeps it out to the off side.
Short and on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara moves back and flicks it towards square leg.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara leans on and blocks it out.
Flighted, full and on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara uses his feet and tucks it towards mid-wicket.
Shortish and on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara moves back and works it towards short mid-wicket.
Another short delivery, on off, Cheteshwar Pujara defends it off the back foot.
Full and on off, shaping in sharply, Shubman Gill knocks it towards short mid-wicket.
Another in-swinger, full and on off, Shubman Gill chops it onto the pitch. This could have easily gone back onto the stumps.

Risky single! This is full and on off, Shubman Gill drives it towards mid off and sets off for the run, the fielder misses his shy at the bowler's end and Gill is safe. Oh..no! It is called a No Ball for overstepping.
Fuller again and outside off, Cheteshwar Pujara steers it through point for a single.
Cameron Green lands this short and on off, Shubman Gill pulls it towards deep square leg for one.
Cameron Green serves this full and way down the leg side, Cheteshwar Pujara leaves it alone and Alex Carey does well to stop it diving to his left.
Overpitched and on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara tucks it towards mid on.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Shubman Gill works it towards short mid-wicket.
Floated, full and on off, Shubman Gill leans on and keeps it out to the off side.
A bit short and on middle, Shubman Gill initialy thinks about playing it on the front foot, but in the moves back and clips it towards short leg.
This keeps really low, on middle, Shubman Gill stays back and manages to put his bat down to negotiate it.
Flighted, full and on off, Shubman Gill moves across and flicks it wide of long on for a single.
Looped up, full and on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara defends it on the front foot.
Cameron Green nails the yorker, on middle, swinging in, Shubman Gill jams it out towards short mid-wicket.

FOUR! Beautiful shot! The first boundary after 96 deliveries. Cameron Green lands this short and around off, Shubman Gill stays there and punches it towards the vacant deep cover fence for a boundary.
FOUR! Two in a row! Cameron Green serves this full and on off, Shubman Gill leans on to his cover drive and times it perfectly wide of mid off for another boundary.
This is pitched up, on middle, Shubman Gill works it off the inner half through square leg for a single.
Back of a length and on off, Cheteshwar Pujara guides it towards cover-point for a run.
Overpitched and on the pads, Shubman Gill whips it towards deep backward square leg for couple of runs. He moves into the 90s!

FOUR! Good shot! Todd Murphy flights this up, on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara skips down the track, makes it a full toss and thrashes it towards the long on fence for a boundary. That also brings up the 100-run partnership between these two batters.
Floated, full and around off, Cheteshwar Pujara pads it away.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara turns it towards short mid-wicket.
Looped up, full and on off, Cheteshwar Pujara prods forward and blocks it down the pitch.
Flatter, full and on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara defends it on the front foot.
Gives this one a bit more air, on middle, Cheteshwar Pujara is solid in his defense again.
Shorter in length and on middle, Shubman Gill moves back and nudges it through mid-wicket for a single.
Short again and on off, Cheteshwar Pujara punches it off the back foot towards covers for a run as Cameron Green stops it with a dive.
Floated, full and on off, Shubman Gill leans on to defend, but gets an inside edge along the ground towards short leg.
Shortish and on middle, Shubman Gill jabs it towards mid on.
Slower through the air, short and on off, turning in, Shubman Gill defends it off the back foot.
Flighted, full and on middle, Shubman Gill gets to the pitch of it and keeps it out well.
Fires this full and on leg, Cheteshwar Pujara clips it towards mid-wicket.
Looped up, full and on off, Cheteshwar Pujara watches it through and keeps it out on the pitch.
Floated, full and on off, Cheteshwar Pujara pushes it back to the bowler.
Bowls this one quicker onto the pads on a fuller length. Cheteshwar Pujara tucks this to square leg.
Floats this one full and onto the pads. Cheteshwar Pujara clips this towards square leg.
Tosses this one full and outside the off pole. Cheteshwar Pujara charges down the wicket and flicks this straight to the fielder at square leg.
Nathan Lyon floats this one full and outside the off stump, Shubman Gill blocks this back to the bowler.

FOUR! This has been absolutely smashed back past the bowler! Nathan Lyon tosses this one full and outside the off pole. Shubman Gill shuffles down the pitch and thumps this straight down the ground for four runs.
Gives the ball air and floats it outside off on a fuller length. Shubman Gill gets well forward and defends solidly.
Loops this full and outside the off stump. Shubman Gill pushes this towards cover.
Flights this full and outside off. Shubman Gill shimmies down the wicket and clips this towards mid-wicket.
Tosses this one full and outside off. Shubman Gill gets ahead once again and flicks this wide of mid-wicket for a single.
Todd Murphy tosses this one full and onto the pads. Shubman Gill flicks this towards mid-wicket.

FOUR! That is HUNDRED for Shubman Gill! What a remarkable inning this has been with his team well behind in the game! Todd Murphy flights this full and going down leg side. Shubman Gill paddles this towards fine leg for four runs and he continues his remarkable form in all formats of the game.
Bowls this short and in line with the stumps. Shubman Gill tucks this to deep square leg for a single.
Tosses this one full and outside leg. Cheteshwar Pujara flicks this towards mid-wicket.
Bowls this one well down leg side. Cheteshwar Pujara opts to leave this one alone.

OUT! PLUMB! Cheteshwar Pujara plays through the long line and wicket just before Tea for Australia! Todd Murphy gets the breakthrough and the 100-run stand comes to an end! This is tossed up full and in line with the stumps. The ball straightens a touch after pitching and beats the inside edge of Cheteshwar Pujara's bat to rap against the pads. The Australian players go up in appeal and the umpire raises his finger. The batter goes for the review and UltraEdge shows no bat involved. Ball Tracking shows three reds and Cheteshwar Pujara will be very disappointed with the dismissal. India are now two down and Australia will be relieved.
Nathan Lyon floats this one full and outside the off stump. Shubman Gill dabs this to the right of the bowler.
Bowls this one slightly short and in line with the stumps. Shubman Gill clips this towards square leg and takes a risky single.
Tosses this one full and just outside the off stump. Virat Kohli is watchful and he defends this back to the bowler.
A flighted delivery bowled full and outside off. Virat Kohli goes hard at the ball and gets an inside edge towards short leg who is unable to hold on.
Beaten! Gets this one to skid through with the arm on a fuller length. Virat Kohli pushes forward once again and the ball goes past the outside edge.

Edged and falls short! Virat Kohli has faced three nervy deliveries but has managed to go survive. This is flighted full and outside off. Virat Kohli looks to get forward and block but gets an outside edge that goes on the bounce to the slip fielder. That will be TEA on DAY 3!
Tossed up, full and on off, Shubman Gill knocks it towards mid off.
Floated, shortish and on off, Shubman Gill leans on and keeps it out to the off side.
Shorter in length and on middle, Shubman Gill moves back and flicks it towards mid-wicket where a misfield allows a single.
Floated, full and on off, Virat Kohli prods forward and defends it onto the pitch.
Quicker, short and on off, Virat Kohli moves back and bunts it to the off side.

A huge appeal for caught behind, but turned down! Todd Murphy flights this up, full and around off, goes with the angle, Virat Kohli leans on block it again, but misses and it goes past the outside edge as Alex Carey pouches it. Steven Smith is asking Carey if he should take the review or not, but no one seems to be confident about it and they decides against it.
Short and on middle, Shubman Gill flicks it off the back foot towards mid-wicket for a single.
Short again and on middle, Virat Kohli moves back and tucks it past short leg.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Virat Kohli turns it towards short mid-wicket.
Floated, full and on middle, Virat Kohli works it towards silly mid on.
Flighted, full and on off, Virat Kohli keeps it out towards silly mid on again.
Quicker, full and on off, Virat Kohli eases it towards long on for a run.
Flatter, full and on middle, Virat Kohli clips it towards short mid-wicket.
Short and on middle, Virat Kohli goes on the back foot and punches it down to long on for a single.
Tossed up, full and on off, Shubman Gill pushes it back to the bowler.
Floated, full and on leg, Shubman Gill works it towards square leg.
Slightly shorter and on middle, Shubman Gill moves back and nudges it towards square leg.

FOUR! Innovative and effective! This is flighted, full and around leg, Shubman Gill goes down and reverse-sweeps it towards the vacant deep point fence for a boundary. However, Todd Murphy won't mind this as he has forced Gill to do something different.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Virat Kohli prods forward and blocks it down the pitch.
Goes short and on middle, Virat Kohli flicks it off the back foot towards square leg.
Good leave! Nathan Lyon flights this up, on off, turning in sharply, Virat Kohli offers no shot at it as the ball goes past the off pole.
Looped up, full and on off, Virat Kohli leans on and pushes it towards short covers.
Flatter, full and on off, Virat Kohli taps it towards point.
Shortish and outside off, Virat Kohli steers it through point for a couple of runs.
Quicker, full and on leg, Shubman Gill works it towards square leg.
Floated, short and down the leg side, Shubman Gill leaves it alone.
Short again and around leg, Shubman Gill tickles it towards fine leg for a single.
Tossed up, full and on off, Virat Kohli prods forward and knocks it to the right of the bowler.
Goes short again and on middle, Virat Kohli moves back and clips it towards short mid-wicket.
Slower through the air, on off, Virat Kohli leans on and taps it towards point. He wants the run, but Gill sends him back.
Short and on middle, Shubman Gill jabs it towards mid on where Marnus Labuschagne from short-mid-wicket runs to his left and,makes a good stop.
Tossed up, full and on off, Shubman Gill drives it towards mid off.
Floated and on off, Shubman Gill steps out and eases it towards long on for a single. 200 uo for India!
Quicker, short and on off, Virat Kohli opens the face of his bat and guides it through backward point for a brace.
Flighted, full and on off, Virat Kohli drills it straight to silly mid on.
Flatter, full and on middle, Virat Kohli drives it towards long on for a run.
Very short and on middle, Virat Kohli moves back and heaves it towards deep mid-wicket for just a single.
Tossed up, full and on off, Shubman Gill taps it in front of short covers and scampers across for a run.
Quicker, short and on middle, Virat Kohli clips it towards mid-wicket.
Floated, full and on middle, Virat Kohli defends it on the front foot.
Goes short again and on middle, Virat Kohli moves back and tucks it towards short mid-wicket again.
Slows it up, short and on off, Virat Kohli watches it through and keeps it out towards point.
Comes from around the wicket and serves a shorter ball on leg stump, Shubman Gill works it off the past the man at leg slip.
Keeps the length short and bowls it on off stump, Gill keeps it out of the back foot.
FOUR! A bit of aggression from Shubman Gill now. Tossed up on middle and leg, Gill skips down the track and heaves it away well in front of mid-wicket for a boundary.
Flatter one on leg stump, tucked away leg side.
Tosses it up a bit and bowls it on middle, Gill defends it off the front foot.
Floated up on the pads, Gill works it just behind square leg for a single.
This is drifted onto middle, Shubman Gill prods and keeps it out.

Sloppy work from Australia and Steven Smith isn't happy. This is flatter and on the pads, Shubman Gill pushes it off the back foot in front of deep mid-wicket for a couple of runs. The throw at the bowler's end is a bit wide and the fielder backing up fumbles allowing the batters to scamper through for the third run.
On off stump, punched back to the bowler.
Sliding it onto the pads, Virat Kohli fails to tickle it 'round the corner.
Full and on off stump, this is knocked down to long off for a single.
On off stump, angling in a bit and Gill pushes it wide of the man at silly point.
This is pitched up around off, angling away, Virat Kohli blocks it off the front foot.
On a hard length and slanted across the right-hnader, Kohli punches it out to cover-point.
Good length around off, Kohli nudges it down in front of point.
FOUR! Nicely driven! This is pitched up around off, Virat Kohli leans on and drives it sweetly to the right of the diving mid on fielder for a boundary.
Length ball, pushed a bit wider of the off stump, Kohli defends it to covers.

FOUR! Poor line from Mitchell Starc and the double-Nelson is up for India! This is bowled around the hips and Virat Kohli just tucks it away behind square on the leg side and the ball runs away into the vacant backward square leg fence.
Tosses it up around middle, Gill leans forward to defend.
A bit slower and shorter on the pads, Gill waits for it and dabs it to the right of mid-wicket for a quick single.
Tossed up full on middle and leg, Virat Kohli drives it straight to extra cover.
Full and at the toes, flicked away to deep mid-wicket for one.
Flighted delivery, full and on leg stump, Shubman Gill pushes it out in front of mid-wicket and picks up a single.
Flatter and around off, Kohli blocks it out.
Pitched up around the fifth stump line and Shubman Gill punches it straight to a widish extra cover.
Back of a length and outside off, tapped away in front of covers for a run.
Fullish length and well outside off, Virat Kohli reaches out and slaps it away to deep cover for a single.
This is full and around off, Gill pushes it on the up to mid off.

Half a shout for run out and they've gone upstairs. This is full again around off, Shubman Gill pushes it toward mid off and sets off for the quick single. Travis Head there score a direct hit at the bowler's end but the replays show that Gill is well in. Not Out!
Good length around off, played toward cover.
Flighted ball outside off, Shubman Gill presses forward and pushes it through cover for a single.
Floats it up on a nagging length outside off, Virat Kohli has a jab at it but gets an inside edge past square leg for a run.
Nagging length again around off, Shubman Gill gets behind the line to make the block.
A bit flatter and around off, blocked out.
Flatter again but a bit shorter around off, Gill works it off the back foot through square leg for one.
FOUR! Overpitched and punished! This is floated full and outside off, Virat Kohli drives it square of the wicket and creams it through cover-point for a boundary.
Length ball well outside off, Gill leans on and plays a checked cover drive to sweeper cover for a single.
Goes full and outside off again from around the wicket, Virat Kohli looks to drive but ends up squeezing it through cover-point for a couple of runs. The 50 partnership is up between these two.
Full again and angling in from around middle, clipped away to short mid-wicket.
FOUR! Runs are flowing here for Virat Kohli and also India. This is short and outside off, Kohli hangs back and steers it down to the vacant third man fence for a boundary.
Pitched up on middle stump, defended toward mid on.
Good length on middle and leg, nudged away through mid-wicket for a single.
This is tossed up on the off stump, Virat Kohli defends it out.
Fullish length around off, Kohli gets on the front foot to defend.
Floats it up now around middle, Virat Kohli whips it toward mid-wicket where the fielder makes a sharp stop.
Shorter one angling across off, Kohli goes on the back foot and pushes it down in front of point.
Nagging length around off, played off the front foot onto the off side.
Maiden! very full on middle and leg, Virat Kohli looks to drive at it but gets an inside edge onto the pads.
Starts off with a shorter one around middle, Shubman Gill shuffles and works it away behind square on the leg side for one.
Tossed up on off stump, blocked out.
Fullish length on off stump, worked away through mid-wicket for one.

OUT! LBW! Just a lapse in concentration from Shubman Gill and Nathan Lyon gets the breakthrough in his first over of a new spell. This is tossed up on a shortish length around off and the ball turns in a bit sharply. Gill goes on the back foot and looks to tuck but misses the ball completely and is rapped on the pads. There is a huge appeal for LBW and the finger is raised! Shubman Gill has reviewed it though. Nothing on UltraEdge. Ball Tracking comes up with three reds and Shubman Gill has to walk back after a sensational inning.
Tossed up full and around middle, this is played toward mid on.
Flighted on the off stump line, Ravindra Jadeja strides forward to defend.
Should have been put away! This is dragged down well outside off, there to be hit, Virat Kohli mistimes th cut shot toward mid off.
Flatter and on the pads, pushed away through mid-wicket for a single.
Floats it up on a length around off, Ravindra Jadeja leans forward to defend.
Flatter and on off stump, kept out toward point.
Angled into middle and leg, Jadeja presses forward to defend but gets an inside edge toward backward square leg.
Drifts it onto middle and leg, Jadeja blocks it out.
Tossed up, full and on off, Virat Kohli leans on and pushes it towards short covers.
Floated, full and on middle, Virat Kohli clips it towards short mid-wicket.
Flatter, full and on off, Virat Kohli guides it towards backward point.
Fires this full and on middle, Virat Kohli whips it wide of short mid-wicket where the fielder only manages to parry it towards long on. They cross.

Floated, full and on off, turning away, Ravindra Jadeja prods forward to defend, but gets an thick outside edge wide of first slip and comes back for the second. However, as he completes the second run, he collides with Travis Head, but no harm done.
Flighted, full and on off, Ravindra Jadeja keeps it out to the off side.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Virat Kohli turns it towards short mid-wicket.
Floated, full and on leg, Virat Kohli clips it towards short mid-wicket.
Slower through the air, on off, Virat Kohli waits for it and steers it towards short third man and scampers across for a single.
Flatter, full and on off, Ravindra Jadeja knocks it towards short covers.

A huge appeal for LBW, but not given! Steven Smith goes for the review. Todd Murphy flights this up, shortish and on off, Ravindra Jadeja prods forward to defend, but gets a thick inside edge onto his pads. UltraEdge confirms that and Australia lose their second review.
Gives this one some air again, on off, Ravindra Jadeja blocks it down the pitch.
Floated, full and on off, Virat Kohli taps it towards backward point.
Tossed up, full and on off, turning in, Virat Kohli leans on and dead bats it. He picks up the ball and gives it to Alex Carey.
Flighted, full and on middle, Virat Kohli defends it on the front foot.
Flatter, full and on middle, Virat Kohli clips it towards short mid-wicket.
Shorter in length and on off, Virat Kohli moves back and keeps it out towards the bowler.
Short again and on middle, Virat Kohli nudges it wide of short mid-wicket for a quick single.
Tossed up, full and on off, Virat Kohli opens the face of his bat and steers it past short third man for a single.
Short and on off, Ravindra Jadeja moves back and punches it towards sweeper covers for a run.
Floated, full and on middle, Virat Kohli drills it towards long on for another run.
Quicker, full and on leg, Ravindra Jadeja flicks it towards backward square leg.
Flighted, full and on off, Ravindra Jadeja blocks it towards short covers.
Darts this one short and on leg, angling in, Ravindra Jadeja works it towards mid on.
Short and on off, Virat Kohli punches it straight to mid off.
Short again and around leg, Virat Kohli nudges it towards short fine leg.
Tossed up, full and on off, Virat Kohli prods forward and blocks it towards short covers.
Goes back to shorter length, on middle, Virat Kohli moves back and tickles it towards short fine leg.
Floated, full and on off, Virat Kohli defends it on the front foot.
Flatter, full and on middle, Virat Kohli moves across and tucks it straight to short mid-wicket. A maiden over from Lyon!
Quicker, short and on middle, Ravindra Jadeja stays back and pushes it back to the bowler.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Ravindra Jadeja blocks it down the pitch.
Floated, full and on middle, Ravindra Jadeja defends it on the front foot.
Flatter, full and on off, Ravindra Jadeja is solid in his defense again.
Darts this one full and on off, Ravindra Jadeja drives it towards short covers.
Two maidens in a row! This is flighted, full and on off, Ravindra Jadeja knocks it to the left of the bowler.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Virat Kohli prods forward and blocks it out.
Floated, full and on off, Virat Kohli opens the face of his bat and steers it towards backward point.
Slower through the air, on middle, Virat Kohli pushes it back to the bowler.
Short and on middle, Virat Kohli moves back and flicks it, but the ball hits Peter Handscomb around his chest at short leg.
Flatter, full and on middle, Virat Kohli turns it towards short mid-wicket.
FOUR! Easy pickings for Kohli! This is short and way down the leg side, Virat Kohli stays there and glances it towards the vacant fine leg fence for a boundary.
Shorter in length and on middle, angling in, Ravindra Jadeja pushes it towards short covers.
Tossed up, full and on off, Ravindra Jadeja keeps it out to the off side.
Floated, full and on middle, Ravindra Jadeja knocks it towards the bowler.
Flatter, full and on off, Ravindra Jadeja drills it towards the bowler where Todd Murphy lets it through, but mid off collects it. Jadeja wants the run, but he is sent back.
Short and on middle, Ravindra Jadeja clips it towards short mid-wicket.
Short again and around off, Ravindra Jadeja punches it wide of short covers. Another maiden over!
Tossed up, full and on off, Virat Kohli steers it towards short third man.
Floated, full and on middle, Virat Kohli moves across and whips it straight to short mid-wicket.
Shortish and on middle, Virat Kohli turns it towards short leg.
Slower through the air, on off, Virat Kohli keeps it out to the off side.
Short again and on middle, Virat Kohli moves back and nudges it onto the ground as the bounce takes it over short leg, but short mid-wicket gathers it.
Darts this one full and on middle, Virat Kohli drills it towards long on for a single.
Flatter, full and on middle, Virat Kohli tucks it through mid-wicket for a single.
Slightly shorter and on off, Ravindra Jadeja punches it through covers for a run.
Short again and on middke, Virat Kohli gets a bit surprised with the extra bounce and nudges it towards square leg.
Floated, full and on middle, Virat Kohli blocks it back to the bowler.
Tossed up, full and on leg, Virat Kohli flicks it through mid-wicket for one.
Slower through the air, on off, Ravindra Jadeja prods forward and defends it towards silly point.
This is floated up on the leg stump line, Virat Kohli nudges it in front of mid-wicket and looks for two but has to settle for one.
Flatter delivery on middle and leg, Ravindra Jadeja hops back to keep it down in front of short leg.

Just making sure. Nicely tossed up by Nathan Lyon, on a nagging length around off and the ball grips and turns away sharply. Ravindra Jadeja looks to defend off the front foot but is beaten past the outside edge and Alex Carey whips off the bails. The umpires go upstairs and the replays show that Jadeja has his back leg planted inside the crease.
This one comes in! A tad quicker and around middle, angling in sharply, Jadeja manages to keep it out with soft hands.
Flatter one around off, tapped away toward point.
Floated on the pads, nudged away to mid-wicket.
Quicker and shorter on middle, Virat Kohli goes deep in his crease to flick it through mid-wicket for a run.
On a nagging length and angled onto the legs, Jadeja gets pushed back but manages to work it past short leg.
Around middle and shorter, the ball comes in sharply and Ravindra Jadeja manages to get a bit of bat on it.
Shorter again around off, pushed away through covers for a single.
Tossed up around middle, Virat Kohli pushes it to silly mid on.
Fired in full and around off, Virat Kohli plays a whippy drive toward wide long on for a single.
Flighted delivery around middle and off, Kohli leans on and works it to short mid-wicket.
On middle, clipped away to mid-wicket.
Good stop! This is floated full and down the leg side, Virat Kohli looks to sweep it fine but mistimes it to the left of the man at leg slip and the fielder makes a sharp stop.

A huge roar from the crowd as Virat Kohli brings up his FIFTY, his first of this series as well! This is shorter on the pads, Kohli works it off the back foot past square leg for a couple of runs. Wait, they are checking for a short run and Kohli might have to wait for his half-century. The replays suggest that Kohli just poked his bat inside the crease and it will be two runs.
Tossed up outside off, pushed away toward cover.
Drops it short on off stump, Kohli has enough time to rock back and tuck it 'round the corner for a single.
This is bowled flatter and around off, Kohli defends it out.
Shorter one over middle, Virat Kohli wrists it away off the back foot past the man at backward square leg for a couple of runs.
A tad shorter on middle and staying low, Kohli keeps it out toward mid on.
Bowled flatter and turning it in from around off, Kohli nudges it toward square leg.
Floated up on middle and leg, worked away to mid-wicket.
Comes from around the stumps now and bowls it fuller around off, Virat Kohli strides out and makes the block.
Starts off with a fullish delivery around off, trying to shape it away, Jadeja gets forward and punches it toward cover.
Very full around off, hint of away movement as well, Jadeja jams it out on the off side.
Full again trying to attack the pads but spills it well down the leg side. Alex Carey with a good take diving to his right.
Length ball around off at 143 clicks, Ravindra Jadeja defends it on the front foot and through the vacant point region for a single.
Length ball on the fifth stump line and just going on with the angle, Kohli leaves it alone.
LEG BYE! Good length around leg stump, Virat Kohli looks to tickle it fine but the ball goes off the pads and down to fine leg. They get a leg bye.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Virat Kohli makes room and drives it towards long off for a single.
Looped up, full and on off, Ravindra Jadeja jams it out towards short covers.

Quicker, full and on middle, Ravindra Jadeja negotiates it well on the front foot. THAT WILL BE STUMPS ON DAY 3!
Cameron Green starts off with a full delivery drifting down leg side. Virat Kohli looks to flick this fine but the ball is far from the bat.
Bowls this on a good length and outside the off stump. Virat Kohli pushes this towards deep cover-point and takes a single.
Comes 'round the wicket to the left-hander and serves this on a good length, outside the off pole. Ravindra Jadeja opts to leave this one alone.
Goes a touch fuller this time but still outside the off stump. Ravindra Jadeja continues to shoulder his arms to it.
Delivers this closer to the off stump on a fuller length. Ravindra Jadeja guides this down to third man and takes his first run of the morning.

Attacks the stumps this time on a fuller length. Virat Kohli flicks this beautifully towards deep mid-wicket. Mitchell Starc gives chase and pulls the ball back inside the boundary rope and the batters pick up a brace.
Todd Murphy floats this one full and into the stumps. Ravindra Jadeja looks to work this leg side and gets a leading edge back towards the bowler.
Flights this one full and outside the off stump. Ravindra Jadeja knocks this towards mid on.

FOUR! First boundary of the morning and it comes from the blade of Ravindra Jadeja! This is bowled slightly short and outside off. Ravindra Jadeja rocks back and cuts this late towards deep backward point for four runs.
Tosses this one into the pads on a fuller length. Ravindra Jadeja blocks this towards mid on.
Bowls this wider outside off on a fuller length. Ravindra Jadeja taps this towards point.
Loops this one full and just outside off. Ravindra Jadeja gets a stride forward and pushes this towards cover.
Nathan Lyon starts off with a shortish delivery spinning into the stumps. Virat Kohli goes deep in the crease and tucks this towards deep square leg and takes a run.
Tosses this one really full and going down leg. Ravindra Jadeja dabs this towards square leg and sets off for a run.
Flights this one full and outside the off pole. Virat Kohli uses the crease and blocks this one out.
Slightly short once again and spinning in from outside off. Virat Kohli clips this towards square leg and takes one. Brings up the 300 for India.
Gets this one to come in with the arm on a shorter length. Ravindra Jadeja looks to work this leg side but misses and gets hit on the pads.
Another skiddy delivery bowled on a shorter length and going down leg. Ravindra Jadeja misses once again and the ball raps high on the pads. A stifled appeal but they do not go up for the review.
Todd Murphy floats this outside off on a fuller length. Virat Kohli dabs this towards point with soft hands and takes a run.
Tosses this one full and in line with the stumps. Ravindra Jadeja blocks this back down the pitch towards the bowler.
Gets this one to skid through on a fuller length and in line with the stumps. Ravindra Jadeja pushes at this and gets an inside edge onto the pads.
This is short and outside the off stump. Ravindra Jadeja rocks back and cuts this hard towards deep point for a single.
Bowls this one a fraction short and outside off. Virat Kohli defends this tentatively into the off side.
Delivers this one closer to the off pole on a fuller length. Virat Kohli blocks this one solidly back down the pitch.
Nathan Lyon floats this one full and into the pads. Ravindra Jadeja defends this into the leg side.
Tosses this one outside the off stump on a fuller length. Ravindra Jadeja pushes at this and gets an inside edge to the leg side.
Flights this one full and on an off-stump line. Ravindra Jadeja defends this back towards the bowler.
Gets this one to come into the stumps from outside off. Ravindra Jadeja stands tall and keeps this one out.
A fraction short and going down leg. Ravindra Jadeja dabs this towards short leg.
Gets this to skid through onto the pads on a shorter length. Ravindra Jadeja goes deep in the crease and whips this towards square leg.
Todd Murphy floats this one full and outside the off stump. Virat Kohli gets across the stumps and flicks this towards deep mid-wicket for one.
Goes full and on an off-stump line. Ravindra Jadeja punches this towards cover.
This is bowled full once again but going down leg. Ravindra Jadeja gets forward to clip this into the leg side but misses and gets hit on the pads. Another stifled appeal.
Tosses this one full and outside off. Ravindra Jadeja eases this towards mid on.
Flighted full and outside the off stump. Ravindra Jadeja looks to force the issue but mistimes his shot to the fielder at mid on.
Loops this one full and in line with the stumps. Ravindra Jadeja gets well forward and blocks this back down the pitch towards the bowler.
Nathan Lyon floats this one full and outside off. Virat Kohli punches this towards mid on.
Flights this one full and outside the off stump. Virat Kohli gets a good stride forward and defends this towards cover.
Tosses this one well outside off on a fuller length. Virat Kohli uses his wrists and clips this towards mid-wicket.
Gets this one closer to the off pole on a fuller length.  Virat Kohli works this to the right of mid-wicket but is unable to get a run.
Loops this one full and outside off. Virat Kohli dabs this into the off side.
Sharp turn into the stumps on a fuller length. The ball stays a fraction low but Virat Kohli is able to tuck this away towards backward square leg.

FOUR! Ravindra Jadeja looking to get a move on here! Todd Murphy tosses this one full and outside the off stump. Ravindra Jadeja gets into the drive and creams this to the left of mid off and finds the straight boundary for four runs.
This is bowled slightly short and close to the off pole. Ravindra Jadeja rocks back and pushes this towards point.
Floats this one full and into the pads. Ravindra Jadeja looks to heave this leg side and miscues his shot just wide of mid on for a single.
Loops this one full and into the stumps. Virat Kohli flicks this towards mid-wicket.
Slightly short this time and into the stumps. Virat Kohli flicks this towards square leg and sets off for a single.

OUT! CAUGHT! Ravindra Jadeja has gifted away his wicket! He has been attempting to play his shots and was not connecting them well but decided to persist with the strategy! Todd Murphy floats this one full and into the stumps. Ravindra Jadeja goes for a heave into the leg side but does not connect this well. The ball lobs up over mid on and Usman Khawaja stretches his hands over his head to grab onto the catch. India lose their fourth wicket and not the start they would have wanted this morning.
Howout: c Usman Khawaja b Todd Murphy

Commentary: Nathan Lyon bowls this short and into the stumps. Virat Kohli clips this towards square leg.
Floats this one full and outside the off stump. Virat Kohli gets forward to defend but the ball spins into his pads and hits him there. The bowler appeals loudly but they do not go for the review.
Tosses this one full and outside the off pole. Virat Kohli smothers this one solidly into the pitch.
Loops this one full and outside off. Virat Kohli dabs this towards cover.
Flights this one full and outside the off stump. Virat Kohli is solid in defense and he pushes this into the off side.
A full delivery fired into the stumps. Virat Kohli turns this towards short mid-wicket and a maiden over to follow the wicket.
Todd Murphy flights this one full and outside off. Srikar Bharat dabs this towards point with soft hands and sets off for a single to open his account.
Floats this one full and into the stumps. Virat Kohli clips this towards mid-wicket.

Tosses this one full and outside off. Virat Kohli taps this towards point and gets a run this time to retain strike.
Nathan Lyon bowls this slightly short and outside off. Virat Kohli eases this down to long on for one.
