Bowls this one slightly short and outside off. Srikar Bharat tucks this towards square leg.
Nathan Lyon getting some turn here as this one comes in sharply from outside off. Srikar Bharat looks to block this but gets beaten on the inside edge. The ball goes off his pads towards first slip.
Tosses this one full and outside the off pole. Srikar Bharat gets well forward and defends this one solidly back to the bowler.
Loopy delivery bowled wider outside off on a fuller length. Srikar Bharat gets a longer stride forward this time and dabs this towards cover.
Floated, short and on middle, Virat Kohli clips it towards short mid-wicket.

Flatter, full and on off, Srikar Bharat goes for the sweep, but gets an inside edge and it goes off the pads towards the short fine leg region. They cross.

Quicker, short and outside off, Srikar Bharat looks to cut it away from his body, but misses it.

Tossed up, full and on off, Virat Kohli turns it towards short leg.
Floated, short and on middle, turns in a long way to the leg side, Virat Kohli thinks about playing it, but leaves it in the end as Alex Carey makes a half-stop.
Flighted, full and on middle, Virat Kohli defends it to the leg side.
Looped up, full and on off, Virat Kohli moves across and works it towards short mid-wicket.
Pushed through quicker, full and on off, Virat Kohli knocks it towards short leg.
A bit short and on middle, keeps low too, Virat Kohli stays back and flicks it through mid-wicket for a single.

Slightly shorter and on leg, Virat Kohli turns it towards backward short leg.
Tossed up, full and on off, Virat Kohli defends it on the front foot.
Flatter, full and on middle, Virat Kohli clips it towards short mid-wicket.

Goes short this time, on middle, Srikar Bharat moves back and knocks it towards short fine leg.
Floated, full and on off, Srikar Bharat prods forward and blocks it towards short covers.
Quicker one, full and on middle, Srikar Bharat gets hurried, but manages to tuck it towards short mid-wicket.
Flighted, full and on middle, Srikar Bharat drives it towards long on for a single.

Shorter in length and on middle, Srikar Bharat taps it on the back foot towards short mid-wicket.
Flatter, full and on off again, Srikar Bharat knocks it towards point.
Shortish and on middle, turning in, Srikar Bharat moves back and flicks it through square leg for a single.
Short again and on middle, Virat Kohli keeps it out towards short mid-wicket.
FOUR! Good shot! Nathan Lyon lands this short and outside off, Srikar Bharat frees his arms and cuts it well through covers for a boundary.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Srikar Bharat leans on and turns it to the leg side.

Shorter in length and on middle, Virat Kohli goes on his back foot and nudges it straight to square leg.
Quicker, short and on off, Srikar Bharat defends it on the back foot.
Tossed up, full and on off, Srikar Bharat get forward and blocks it towards short covers.

Bowls this slightly short and outside the off. Virat Kohli rocks back and punches this towards mid on.

Gets this one to skid through into the pads on a fuller length. Virat Kohli misses his block and gets hit on the pads. A massive appeal but no review.
Delivers this in line with the stump on a fuller length. Virat Kohli blocks this back to the bowler.
Maiden over to start off for Matthew Kuhnemann. This is slightly short and straight. Virat Kohli just about manages to keep this out.
Nathan Lyon floats this full and outside the off stump. Srikar Bharat clips this towards deep square leg for a single.
Tosses this one full and outside the off stump. Virat Kohli dabs this towards cover.
Continues to flight this full and outside off. Virat Kohli blocks this back down the pitch towards the bowler.
Loops this one full and outside off. Virat Kohli continues to be defensive and keeps this one out.
Goes full once again and just outside off. Virat Kohli defends this back towards the bowler.
Bowls this one slightly short and spinning into the stumps. Virat Kohli flicks this towards deep square leg and they pick up a couple of runs.
Matthew Kuhnemann floats this one full and outside off. Srikar Bharat blocks this solidly towards cover.
Delivers this in line with the stumps on a fuller length. Srikar Bharat dabs this back down the pitch.
Fires this one full and into the stumps. Srikar Bharat taps this watchfully towards cover.
Goes really full this time and at the stumps. Srikar Bharat pushes this towards short cover.
Loops this one full and outside the off stump. Srikar Bharat knocks this to the fielder at short cover once again.
Bowls this one in line with the stumps on a fuller length. Srikar Bharat gets a good stride forward and defends this back to the bowler.
Nathan Lyon goes 'round the wicket and fires this short and into the pads. Virat Kohli misses his flick and gets hit on the pads.
This is short and into the pads. Virat Kohli tucks this towards backward square leg and sets off for a single. There is a throw at the stumps and they take two more on over throws.
Floats this one full and outside off. Srikar Bharat blocks this towards cover.
Tosses this one full as well and wider outside off. Srikar Bharat dabs this towards backward point.
Slightly short this time and outside the off pole. Srikar Bharat looks to push at this and gets and inside edge towards the keeper.
Loops this one full and outside off. Srikar Bharat goes for the sweep shot but misses and gets hit on the pads but his stride is well outside the off stump.
Matthew Kuhnemann tosses this one full and on a leg-stump line. Virat Kohli taps this back towards the bowler.
Bowls this one full and into the pads. Virat Kohli clips this down to fine leg and picks up a couple of runs.
Tosses this one full and outside off. Virat Kohli knocks this to the left of mid on and rushes for a single.
Goes really full this time and going down leg. Srikar Bharat flicks this towards the fielder at mid-wicket.
Loops this one full and in line with the stumps. Srikar Bharat makes room and strokes this towards cover.
Gets this one to skid through with the arm on a fuller length and in line with the stumps. Srikar Bharat gets forward in defense and gets an inside edge into the leg side.
Cameron Green bowls this full and angles this in from outside off. Virat Kohli keeps his head still and flicks this towards mid-wicket.
On a good length this time but strays onto the pads. Virat Kohli clips this towards deep square leg and takes a single.
Delivers this on a fuller length and attacks the stumps. Srikar Bharat blocks this towards mid on.
Continues to bowl full and outside the off stump. Srikar Bharat pushes this towards mid off and sets off for a quick run.
Bangs this one in short and outside the off stump. Virat Kohli drops his wrists and sways out of the way to let the ball go through to the keeper.
Decides to bowl this on a good length and outside the off pole. Virat Kohli knocks this towards the fielder at short cover.
Matthew Kuhnemann floats this one full and in line with the stumps. Srikar Bharat defends this back towards the bowler.
Loops this one just outside off on a fuller length. Srikar Bharat gets forward in defense and taps it into the leg side.
Tosses this one at the stumps on a fuller length. Srikar Bharat is watchful as he pushes this towards short cover.
Flighted full and outside the off stump. Srikar Bharat eases this down to long off for an easy run.
A low full toss bowled at the stumps. Virat Kohli whips this towards deep mid-wicket and collects a single.
Another floated delivery bowled full and outside off. Srikar Bharat drives this towards deep cover and takes one.
Cameron Green Bowls this on a good length and outside off. Srikar Bharat dabs this towards cover and looks for a run that is not there.
Angles this one down leg on a fuller length. Srikar Bharat looks to flick this away but misses and gets hit on the pads. The ball rolls towards square leg and they take an extra.
Goes full once again and attacks the pads. Virat Kohli clips this down to fine leg for a single.
Bowls this on a yorker length and just outside the off pole. Srikar Bharat gets his bat down in time and digs the ball out back towards the bowler.
Delivers this on a fuller length and outside the off stump. Srikar Bharat knocks this towards cover.
Continues to bowl full and angles this in from outside off. Srikar Bharat hits this firmly but straight to the fielder at mid off.
Matthew Kuhnemann floats this one full and into the stumps. Virat Kohli knocks this back to the bowler.
A low full toss bowled on the pads. Virat Kohli flicks this towards deep backward square leg and collects a couple of runs. Brings up the 350 for India.
Flights this one full and in line with the stumps. Virat Kohli dabs this towards square leg and sets off for a run.
Angles this into the pads on a fuller length. Srikar Bharat manages to get this down to fine leg and picks up a brace.
Tosses this one full and at the stumps. Srikar Bharat gets a confident stride forward and defends this back to the bowler.
Loops this one full and outside the off stump. Srikar Bharat blocks this to the fielder at cover.
Cameron Green bowls this on a good length and outside the off stump. Virat Kohli defends this well towards cover.
Goes really full this time and into the stumps. Virat Kohli flicks this towards mid-wicket.
On a good length this time and outside off. Virat Kohli dabs this towards short mid-wicket.

FOUR BYES! Cameron Green bangs this in short with the keeper up to the wicket. Virat Kohli sways out of the way but Alex Carey is unable to react quickly enough. The ball hits the gloves but runs away to the fence for four extra runs.
Goes back to bowling on a good length and outside off. Virat Kohli punches this towards deep cover and takes a couple of runs.
Bowls this one back of a length and outside off. Virat Kohli stands tall and blocks this on out into the off side.
Matthew Kuhnemann tosses this one full and into the stumps. Srikar Bharat blocks this back to the bowler.
Loops this one full and outside off. Srikar Bharat strokes this towards deep cover for a single.
Tosses this one full and outside off. Virat Kohli pushes this towards cover.
Angles this into the pads on a fuller length. Virat Kohli clips this towards square leg and takes a run.
Flights this one full and in line with the stumps. Srikar Bharat eases this down to long off for one.
Another tossed-up delivery bowled at the stumps on a fuller length. Virat Kohli dabs this back towards the bowler. That will be LUNCH on DAY 4!
Cameron Green starts with a well-directed bouncer, on middle, Srikar Bharat ducks undreneath it.
A slower bouncer now, on middle and leg, Srikar Bharat once again ducks under it.
This looks like a plan from Australia as Cameron Green bangs in another bouncer, on middle and leg, Srikar Bharat bends down and lets it go to the keeper.
Fourth bouncer in a row! Cameron Green delivers this short and on middle, Srikar Bharat ducks again.
It looks like Cameron Green and Alex Carey are playing at the moment. Green comes around the wicket and bowls another bouncer on leg, Srikar Bharat once again ducks.
Guess what? A maiden over with six bouncers! This is short and on leg again, Srikar Bharat ducks well again.
Tossed up, full and on off, Virat Kohli leans on and defends it towards short third man.
Floated, full and on middle, Virat Kohli turns it towards short mid-wicket.
Flighted around middle, turning in with some bounce, Virat Kohli gets surpsied by it and nudges it towards short fine leg for a single.
Flatter, full and on off, Srikar Bharat pushes it to the left of short covers and scamper across for a run.
Quicker, full and on middle, Virat Kohli tucks it wide of mid-wicket for another run. He moves to the 90s!
Looped up, full and on off, Srikar Bharat strides forward and defends it to the off side.
Cameron Green bangs another bouncer, on middle, angling away, Virat Kohli sways away from it.
Short of a length and around leg, Virat Kohli pulls it towards fine leg for a single.
SIX! BANG! Cameron Green lands this short and on middle, Srikar Bharat is ready for it this time and swivels and pulls it over the deep mid-wicket fence for a biggie.

SIX! Srikar Bharat is taking on Green now! Cameron Green tries another bouncer, but this sits up nicely around leg, Srikar Bharat once again swivels and pulls it way over the deep square leg fence for another maximum.

FOUR! Fine shot! Cameron Green bowls this back of a length and outside off with no protection in the deep, Srikar Bharat accepts the width and cuts it towards deep point for a boundary now. Also, it is called a No Ball for overstepping. The lead of Australia is under 100 now!
Goes fuller and on middle, Srikar Bharat drives it towards mid on. Oh..no! It is called a No Ball again for overstepping.
Short and on middle, Srikar Bharat pulls it towards deep mid-wicket for a run.
21 runs off the over! This is short again and on leg, Virat Kohli controls his pull towards fine leg for one more.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Virat Kohli turns it towards short mid-wicket.
A bit short and on middle, Virat Kohli moves back and clips it towards short mid-wicket.
A full toss, on middle, Virat Kohli eases it towards long on for a single.
In the air...safe! This is floated, full and on middle, Srikar Bharat goes for the sweep, but gets a top edge. However, it lands safely in the vacant short fine leg region. They cross.
Shortish and on off, Virat Kohli defends it on the back foot.
Another short delivery, on off, Virat Kohli moves across and flicks it towards square leg for a run.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Virat Kohli tucks it towards deep square leg and comes back for the second.
Flatter, full and on off, Virat Kohli opens the face of his bat and steers it towards backward point.
Floated, full and on middle, Virat Kohli works it towards long on for a single. He moves to 97!
Slightly shorter and on off, Srikar Bharat goes on the front foot, but adjust well to keep it out towards backward point.
Flighted, short and on off, Srikar Bharat defends it on the front foot again.
Looped up, full and on off, Srikar Bharat negotiates it well.
Floated, short and on middle, turning in, Virat Kohli tickles it towards short fine leg.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Virat Kohli turns it towards short leg.
Goes short again and on middle, Virat Kohli moves back and flicks it towards deep square leg for a single.

OUT! TAKEN! Nathan Lyon strikes! Australia finally breaks this partnership which was looking really good. Lyon flights this up around middle, turning in a bit, Srikar Bharat prods forward to defend with hard hands, but the extra bounce and turn takes the inside edge as the ball loops up of his pads towards short leg where Peter Handscomb takes a dolly. Bharat is really disappointed as he misses out on a well-deserved half-century.
Howout: c Peter Handscomb b Nathan Lyon

Commentary: Tossed up, full and on off, Axar Patel pushes it towards short covers.
Looped up, full and on off, Axar Patel drives it straight to short covers again.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Virat Kohli whips it towards mid-wicket where the fielder dives to his left and parries it to mid on. They cross. Kohli moves to 99!
Slower through the air, on leg, angling in, Axar Patel looks to defend, but misses and gets hit on the pads as the ball goes nowhere.
Floated, full and on middle, Axar Patel blocks it back to the bowler.
Flatter, full and on middle, Axar Patel defends it on the front foot.
A bit short and on middle, Axar Patel stays back and knocks it down the pitch.
Looped up, full and around off, Axar Patel looks to drive it, but gets an inside edge towards backward square leg.
Shortish and on leg, Virat Kohli flicks it straight to square leg.

The wait is over! Virat Kohli has reached his 28th century in Test cricket and it has been a long time coming! The crowd is absolutely ecstatic as they have come in large numbers to witness this landmark and he looks like a relieved man. Nathan Lyon floats this one full and in line with the stumps. Virat Kohli clips this towards deep square leg and takes a single. He removes his helmet and kisses the locket he is wearing as his celebrations are quite muted for someone so animated. What a patient and well-constructed knock this has been.
FOUR! Nice shot! Nathan Lyon lands this short and well outside off, Axar Patel goes on his back foot and cuts it through point for a boundary.
Tossed up, full and on off, Axar Patel drives it towards silly mid off where the fielder lets it through and allows a run. 400 up for India!
Darts this one full and on middle, Virat Kohli clips it towards backward short leg.
Flatter, full and on middle, turning in, Virat Kohli does well to get some bat on it and nudges it towards square leg.
This is on a good length and around off, shaping in, Axar Patel tries to push it away, but gets an inside edge onto his pads.
Goes fuller this time, on leg, shaping in, Axar Patel misses his flick and Alex Carey gathers it behind the stumps.
Full again and down the leg again, angling in, Axar Patel misses his flick again. Starc need to correct his line a bit to use the reverse swing.
Mitchell Starc pitches it up, on middle, shaping in, Axar Patel knocks it towards mid on.
Touch fuller and outside off, Axar Patel lifts his bat and lets it go to the keeper.
A maide over! This is on a good length and on middle, Axar Patel plays it back towards the bowler.
Flatter, full and on off, Virat Kohli moves back and keeps it out to the off side.
Shorter in length and on off, Virat Kohli moves back and clips it towards short leg.
Tossed up, full and on off, turning in, Virat Kohli leans on to defend, but the extra bounce takes the inside edge and goes on the bounce towards short leg.
Shortish again and outside off, Virat Kohli defends it on the back foot.
Flighted, full and on middle, Virat Kohli tucks it towards short mid-wicket.
Looped up, full and on off, Virat Kohli opens the face of his bat and steers it towards the vacant third man regions as Travis Head runs after it and mops it up. Two runs taken!
Mitchell Starc bowls this slightly back of a length and outside off. Axar Patel leaves this one alone.
On a good length this time and closer to the off pole. Axar Patel punches this towards deep point for a single.
Bowls this really full and way outside the off stump. Virat Kohli reaches for it but misses.

FOUR! This is an absolutely gorgeous shot! The first boundary for Virat Kohli on Day 4! Mitchell Starc bowls a low full toss outside the off stump. Virat Kohli punches this down to long off for four runs.
Goes back to bowling on a good length and outside off. Virat Kohli knocks this towards cover.

FOUR! The second boundary in the over and Virat Kohli looks to be getting a move on here! Mitchell Starc strays onto the pads on a fuller length. Virat Kohli flicks this down to fine leg for four more runs.
Nathan Lyon floats this one full and into the pads. Axar Patel gets forward and blocks this towards backward point.
Slightly short and into the stumps. Axar Patel rocks back and punches this to short cover.
Goes over the wicket now and flights this full outside off. Axar Patel opts to leave this one alone.
Bowls this full and in line with the stumps. Axar Patel goes on the back foot and punches this to deep cover for a single.
Flights this one full and outside the off stump. Virat Kohli gets forward and dabs this towards short leg.
Loops this one full and into the stumps. Virat Kohli clips this towards square leg. Just one run from the over.
Mitchell Starc goes full but strays down leg side. Axar Patel looks to flick this fine but misses and Alex Carey has to dive to his right to collect the ball.
FOUR! Easy pickings for Axar Patel and runs are now starting to come easy for India! Mitchell Starc fires this one full and into the pads. Axar Patel glances this down to fine leg for four runs.
On a fuller length once again but attacks the stumps this time. Axar Patel knocks this towards mid-wicket.
Bowls this one wide outside off on a good length. Axar Patel is watchful as he leaves this one alone.
A touch too full from Mitchell Starc once again and onto the pads. Axar Patel flicks this towards deep mid-wicket and a good stop from Todd Murphy at the boundary keeps them down to three runs.
Delivers this on a good length and outside the off stump. Virat Kohli shoulders his arms to this one.
Nathan Lyon floats this one full and into the pads. Some extra bounce off the surface once again surprises the batter but he manages to block it out towards backward point.
Angles this into the legs on a fuller length. Axar Patel misses his block and the ball balloons off his pads into the leg side.
Flights this one full and outside the off stump. Axar Patel knocks this towards cover.
Loopy delivery bowled full and on an off-stump line. Axar Patel dabs this down towards backward point.
Bowls this one slightly short and into the stump. Axar Patel rocks back and defends this towards short cover.
A tossed-up delivery bowled just outside the off pole. Axar Patel is well forward as he blocks this solidly into the off side.
Todd Murphy tosses this one full and on a leg-stump line. Virat Kohli blocks this towards mid-wicket.
Slightly short and onto the pads. Virat Kohli whips this towards square leg on his back foot.
Short once again and outside off. Virat Kohli misses out as he pulls this straight to mid-wicket.
FOUR! Gets this one away well! Another short ball was delivered outside the off stump. Virat Kohli is deep in the crease as he pulls this towards deep square leg for four runs.
Goes full now and in line with the stumps. Virat Kohli clips this towards mid-wicket and collects a single.
Beaten! This is flighted full and just outside off, Axar Patel plays the wrong line and the ball straightens after pitching. It swishes past the outside edge.
Nathan Lyon bowls this full and outside the off stump. Virat Kohli goes deep in the crease and blocks this into the off side.
Slightly short and in line with the stumps. Virat Kohli rocks back and flicks this towards square leg.
Another shortish delivery bowled at the stumps. Virat Kohli tucks this towards square leg.
FOUR! A fine shot from Virat Kohli as he finds the fence once again! Nathan Lyon bowls a low full toss outside the off stump. Virat Kohli reaches for it and knocks it towards long off for four runs.
Strays onto the pads on a fuller length. Virat Kohli clips this towards fine leg for a couple of runs.
On a shortish length once again and pitching outside leg. Virat Kohli goes on the back foot and dabs this towards backward square leg.

SIX! That has just about managed to go over the ropes for a maximum! Todd Murphy loops this one full and outside off. Axar Patel goes inside out and lofts this towards long off. Usman Khawaja is at the boundary and grabs hold of the catch but steps on the ropes which makes him trip over. Six runs added to Axar Patel's kitty.
Bowls this one full and into the stumps. Axar Patel tucks this into the leg side.
On a shortish length and angled in from outside off. Axar Patel goes on the back foot and cuts this towards point for a single.
Tosses this one full and outside the off stump. Virat Kohli smothers this down into the pitch.

FOUR! This has been placed in the gap to perfection! Todd Murphy floats this one full and on middle stump. Virat Kohli flicks this wide of mid on and the ball races away to the cow corner boundary for four runs. Usman Khawaja gives chase but the catch attempt seems to have damaged his leg and he limps out to get treatement.
Floated full and at the stumps. Virat Kohli goes back and clips this into the leg side.
Nathan Lyon flights this one full and outside the off stump. Axar Patel dabs this towards backward point.
Strays onto the pads on a fuller length. Axar Patel flicks this down to fine leg for a couple of runs.
Tosses this one full and outside the off pole. Axar Patel dabs this down to point.
Goes over the stumps now and fires this into the stumps on a fuller length. Axar Patel pushes this towards cover-point.
Bowls this one short and outside the off pole. Axar Patel slaps this towards deep point and collects a single.
Loops this one full and on a leg-stump line. Virat Kohli dabs this towards short leg.
Todd Murphy bowls this one slightly short and into the stumps. Axar Patel rocks back and punches this towards extra cover.
Short once again and just outside off. Axar Patel is unable to find the gap as he pushes this towards extra cover once again.
Floats this one full and outside off. Axar Patel blocks this solidly towards short cover.
Tosses this one full and angled into the stumps. Axar Patel gets a confident stride forward and keeps the ball out.
Drops this one short once again and outside off. Axar Patel looks to punch this away but finds the fielder at extra cover.
Flights this one full and wide outside the off pole. Axar Patel chooses to leave this one alone. A maiden over from Todd Murphy.
Tossed up, full and on off, Virat Kohli leans on and defends it towards short covers.
Short and around off, Virat Kohli moves back and keeps it out towards short covers.
Flighted, full and on middle, Virat Kohli blocks it towards the bowler.
Goes short again and on middle, Virat Kohli clips it off the back foot towards wide mid on for a single.
Flatter, full and on off, turning in, Axar Patel stays back and keeps it out to the off side.
Floated, full and on off, Axar Patel is solid in his defense again.
Flatter, full and down the leg, Virat Kohli tucks it towards backward square leg for a single.
Quicker, short and on off, angling in, Axar Patel goes back and pushes it towards short covers.
Short again and on middle, Axar Patel nudges it towards short mid-wicket.
Flighted, full and on middle, Axar Patel defends it on the front foot.
Looped up, full and on middle, Axar Patel drives it towards wide of mid on for a run.
Slower through the air, on leg, turning in, Virat Kohli leaves it alone.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Axar Patel uses his feet and whips it wide of deep mid-wicket for a couple of runs.
Floated, full and on off, Axar Patel prods forward and defends it to the off side.
Goes short and on middle, Axar Patel moves back and tucks it towards short mid-wicket.
FOUR! Nice shot! Matthew Kuhnemann lands this short and way outside off, Axar Patel moves back quickly and punches it through covers for a boundary.
Flatter, full and on leg, Axar Patel drills it towards long on for a single.
Shortish and on middle, Virat Kohli moves back and flicks it through mid-wicket for one.
Travis Head starts with a tossed up delivery, full and on off, turning in, Virat Kohli blocks it out.
Floated, full and on off, Virat Kohli defends it on the front foot.
Flighted, full and on off, Virat Kohli leans on and taps it in front of short covers for quick single.
Slower through the air, on off, turning away, Axar Patel leaves it alone.
Flatter, full and on middle, Axar Patel drives it back to the bowler.
Looped up, full and around off, Axar Patel drives it sweetly through covers and wide of long off for just a run.
Short and on leg, Axar Patel heaves it towards deep backward square leg for a single.
Short again and on middle, Virat Kohli moves back and jabs it towards deep mid-wicket for one.
Matthew Kuhnemann continues to bowl short and on leg, Axar Patel forces it towards deep backward square leg for one.
Flatter, full and on middle, Virat Kohli turns it towards short mid-wicket.
Good running! This one is darted full and on the pads, Virat Kohli clips it towards wide of deep square leg and comes back for the second.
Tossed up, full and on off, Virat Kohli drives it wide of short covers where Marnus Labuschagne dives to his right to stop it.
EDGED BUT SAFE! Travis Head lands this short and outside off, Axar Patel looks to cut it, but gets a thick outside edge over the first slip fiedler for just a single.
Short again and on middle, Virat Kohli moves back and flicks it towards deep mid-wicket for a run.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Axar Patel blocks it back to the bowler.
Floated, full and on off, Axar Patel pushes it to the bowler again.
Quicker one, on middle, keeps low too, Axar Patel manages to put his bat down in time to keep it out.
Fligthed, full and on off, Axar Patel uses his feet and drives it towards long on for an easy one.
Just short! This is tossed up, full and on leg, turning in, Axar Patel looks to flick it, but gets an inside edge which just falls short of Steven Smith at leg slip.
Floated, full and on leg, Axar Patel clips it towards short mid-wicket.
Flatter, full and on leg, Axar Patel nudges it towards square leg.
Quicker, shortish and on leg, turning in, Axar Patel looks to whip it away, but misses.
Flighted, full and on middle, Axar Patel blocks it down thr pitch.

FOUR BYES! Matthew Kuhnemann bowls this a bit quicker, full and on leg, turning in with extra bounce, Axar Patel misses his flick and Alex Carey behind the stumps fails to stop it as the ball races to the fine leg fence for a boundary.
Tossed up, full and on off, Virat Kohli prods forward and blocks it out.
Floated, full and on off, Virat Kohli keeps it out to the off side.
Slower through the air, on off, turning in, Virat Kohli looks to defend, but gets an inside edge to the leg side.
Flatter, full and on middle, Virat Kohli nudges it through square leg for a single.
Short and outside off, Axar Patel punches it towards sweeper covers for a run. India trail by under 10 runs now!
Flighted, full and on off, Virat Kohli drives it through covers for another run. THAT WILL BE TEA ON DAY 4!
Starts off from around the wicket and bowsl it full on the pads, Virat Kohli glances it down to fine leg and picks up a couple of runs.
Nicely bowled! Slows it up and drifts it across the off stump, Kohli looks to defend off the front foot but is beaten past the outside edge.
A touch shorter on off stump, Kohli gets behind the line and makes the block.
Quick run! Tossed up on the legs, Virat Kohli flicks it to mid-wicket and scampers through for a quick single, good running.
Bowls it flatter on middle and leg, pushed off the back foot toward mid on.
Floats it up around off and middle, Axar Patel leans forward to defend.
Tosses it up full and on leg stump, flicked away straight to mid-wicket.
On off stump, Kohli strides forward to make the block.
Gives it a nice loop and bowls it full on the toes, Virat Kohli wrists it toward mid-wicket.
Shorter one on middle, Kohli nudges it down in front of mid-wicket.
Flatter and on the pads, tucked away off the back foot to backward square leg.
Uppish but wide of the man! Tossed up on leg stump, Virat Kohli flicks it to the left of a diving Cameron Green at short mid-wicket and gets it down to wide long on for a single.
Quicker and shorter down leg, Virat Kohli flicks it behind square on the leg side and picks up a couple of runs.
Keeps the length short and around leg stump, Kohli goes on the back foot and keeps it down to the right of short leg.
Flatter one around leg, keeping a touch low, Virat Kohli flicks it away in front of square leg and comes back for the second with ease. The scores are now level!
Floated up around leg stump, Kohli pushes it to the left of short leg who gets a hand on it.
On middle and off, Kohli leans forward to defend.
Flighted delivery on the legs, wristed away to square leg.
Fired in around off, driven firmly but straight to cover.
Floated up around off, Axar Patel pushes it toward a deepish cover fielder.
Looks to slide one in from around off, Patel keeps it out toward mid on.
FOUR! Cut away and India are finally in the lead! Drops it short and outside off, Axar Patel rocks back and cuts it hard into the vacant point fence.
Quicker one around off, bouncing a bit extra, Axar Patel does well to keep it down past point and the batters pick up a quick single.
Floated up on middle and leg, Kohli reaches out and works it in front of mid-wicket for a single.
Shorter one on leg stump, Virat Kohli pulls it firmly off the back foot to deep mid-wicket for a run.

DROPPED! A really tough chance goes down! Nathan Lyon tosses it up on a length around off and gets the ball to grip and bite off the deck. Axar Patel gets taken aback and gets a dab on it very late. The ball goes quickly past the keeper and an unsighted Steven Smith sticks out a right hand but the ball goes off his palms and toward third man. They get a couple of runs.
Flatter delivery, angling into middle and leg and staying low. Axar Patel pulls it in front of square on the leg side and picks up two more.
Stays low again! Flatter on middle, keeping low, Patel manages to keep it out on the off side.
A bit fuller and on off stump, played away toward cover.
Flighted delivery around middle, Axar Patel defends it with soft hands.
On a good length and well wide of the off stump, left alone by Kohli.
Length ball angling in from outside off, Virat Kohli punches it on the up to mid off.

FOUR! Begging to be hit and put away nicely by Virat Kohli. Overpitched but well outside off, Kohli reaches out and smashes it through extra cover for a boundary. The 100-run stand is up between these two as well.

FOUR! Another boundary, this time on the on-side and that will be 150 for Virat Kohli, a classy knock from him. Pitched up on middle and leg, Kohli pushes it through wide mid on and the ball just races into the fence.
Full and wide outside off, eased away through cover-point for a single and the 500 is now up for India, they lead by 20 runs.
Comes from around the wicket and serves a length ball in that channel around off. Axar Patel shoulders arms at it.
Quicker and on leg stump, Kohli solidly keeps it out.
Slower and shorter on off stump, worked away off the back foot through square leg for one.
Nicely bowled! Nagging length around off and middle, spearing it in a bit. Axar Patel gets pushed on the back foot and just about manages to get his bat down in time.
Quicker and flatter angling in from middle, Axar Patel keeps it out.
Keeps firing it in around middle, Patel defends it out from inside his crease.
Fraction shorter around off, cut away firmly off the back foot to deep point for one.
Fullish length around the fifth stump line, left alone for the keeper to collect.
Good length outside off, steered away down to third man for a single by Axar Patel.
A juicy full toss outside off, Virat Kohli gets across but punches it straight to mid off.
On a hard length pushed well outside the off stump, Virat Kohli lets it go.
FOUR! An attempted yorker that turns out to be a waist-high full toss, Virat Kohli looks to drive but gets an outside edge that runs down to the third man fence for a boundary.
Gets it full and wide this time, Kohli reaches out and squeezes it down to third man for a run.
Flatter one angling across the right-hander ans staying a touch low, Kohli gets deep in his crease and keeps it out on the leg side.
On the pads, flicked away to square leg.
FOUR! Just a fraction shorter and Virat Kohli latches onto it. This is bowled on off stump, Kohli pulls it uppishly to the left of a diving fielder at square leg for a boundary.
On middle and off, kept out by Kohli.
FOUR! Sweetly timed! Floated full and around middle, Virat Kohli just leans forward and pushes it firmly to the right of mid off and the fielder from long on can't reach it either. Another boundary!
Misses out! This is fired in down the leg side, Kohli sets up for the hard sweep behind square leg but misses.

This is flighted on the pads, Axar Patel works it away in front of square leg for a single and there is a huge roar from the crowd. Patel brings up his third FIFTY of the series and soaks in the applause from the home crowd.
Floated up on off stump, Kohli leans forward and plays it with soft hands behind point for a quick run.
Quicker one around off, sliced away toward backward point.
On middle, Patel strides forward to block.
Tossed up on off stump, Patel pushes it off the front foot to mid off.
Shorter in length outside off, Axar Patel cuts it through the point region for a single.
Floated, short and on leg, keeps low too, Axar Patel looks to pull it away, but misses.
Tossed up around leg, turning in to the leg side, Axar Patel leaves it alone.
SIX! Huge hit! This is flighted, full and on middle, Axar Patel goes down and heaves it well over the wide deep mid-wicket fence for a biggie.
Short and outside off, Axar Patel steers it through backward point for a couple of runs.

Flatter, full and aroud leg, Axar Patel paddles it wide of fine leg where Matt Renshaw runs to his left and dives to make a good stop. He throws it towards the keeper who turns it towards the bowler, but Kohli makes it safely for the second run.
Shorter in length and on middle, Axar Patel moves back and keeps it out towards short mid-wicket.
Short and on middle, Virat Kohli tucks it towards short mid-wicket.
Floated, full and around off, Virat Kohli dabs it towards point.
Goes short again and on middle, Virat Kohli nudges it towards mid-wicket for a single.
Short again and outside off, Axar Patel cuts it towards sweeper covers for a run.
Slower through the air and on off, straightens after hitting the surface, Virat Kohli looks to drive it, but gets an outside edge towards the vacant third man fence for three runs.
FOUR! Lovely shot! This is flighted, full and on off, Axar Patel goes down on one knee and nails his slog-sweep towards the deep mid-wicket fence for a boundary.
Short and on middle, Virat Kohli forces it straight to short mid-wicket.
Tossed up, full and on off, Virat Kohli drives it towards long off for a single.

SIX! Up, up and away! This is looped up, full and on off, Axar Patel once again goes down and slogs it over the deep mid-wicket fence for another maximum. India have changes their gears and the runs are flowing now.
Quicker, short and on off, Axar Patel pushes it back to the left of the bowler.
Flatter, full and on middle, Axar Patel turns it to the leg side.

SIX! 13 runs off the over! Axar Patel is hitting it out of the park pretty easily here. This is tossed up, full and on off, Axar Patel picks up the length early and smashes it over the deep mid-wicket fence for a maximum.
Floated, full and on the pads, Virat Kohli whips it towards deep mid-wicket for a single.
Flatter, full and on leg, Axar Patel drives it towards long on for a run.
Short and on middle, Virat Kohli moves back and pushes it towards silly mid on.
Slower through the air, on middle, Virat Kohli watches it through and keeps it out to the leg side.
Slightly shorter and on middle, Virat Kohli clips it towards mid-wicket.
Flighted. full and on off, Virat Kohli taps it in front of short covers for one more.
This is pitched up, on off, angling in, Virat Kohli blocks it back to the bowler.
On a length and on off, Virat Kohli guides it through covers for a single. The scoreboard reads 555/5!

OUT! DRAGGED ON! Mitchell Starc strikes! Axar Patel is a bit unlucky, but he will have to go back to the hut. Starc lands this on a good length and around off, shaping in a bit, Axar Patel stays in his crease and tries to drive it away from his body, but gets an inside edge back onto the stumps as the bails go flying. He is disappointed as it was a great opportunity for him to score a hundred. India six down now!
Back of a length and on leg, Ravichandran Ashwin nudges it through square leg for a single and gets off the mark.
Back of a length again, on middle, Virat Kohli tucks it towards short mid-wicket.
Short and on middle, slower too, Virat Kohli pulls it towards deep square leg for a run.
Short and on middle, Virat Kohli moves back and clips it towards deep mid-wicket for a single.
Tossed up, full and on fof, Ravichandran Ashwin drives it wide of mid off where Mitchell Starc slides to his left to stop it as the batters scampers across for run.
Floated, short and on off, Virat Kohli leans and keeps it out to the off side.
Short and on middle, Virat Kohli nudges it straight to square leg.
Todd Murphy slows it up, on middle, turns in with extra bounce, Virat Kohli tickles it towards short fine leg where a fumble allows another run.
Flighted, full and on off, Ravichandran Ashwin defends it on the front foot.
This is on a good length and down the leg side, Virat Kohli misses his flick as Alex Carey collects it behind the stumps.
Length again and on middle, Virat Kohli nudges it towards deep mid-wicket for a brace.
Goes fuller and on middle, drills it towards deep mid-wicket for a run.
Pulls his length back a bit, on off, Ravichandran Ashwin dabs it towards point.
Touch fuller and down the leg side, Ravichandran Ashwin misses his flick.
Back of a length and on leg, Ravichandran Ashwin flicks it towards deep mid-wicket for one more.
FOUR! Nicely played! This is tossed up, full and around off, Ravichandran Ashwin strides forward and drives it firmly through covers for a boundary.
Floated, short and on off, turning in shaprly with extra bounce, Ravichandran Ashwin moves back to defend, but gets surprised by the bounce as the ball hits the bat and rolls towards point.
Flighted, full and on off, turning in, Ravichandran Ashwin leans on to block, but misses and gets hit on the pads.
Short and on off, Ravichandran Ashwin moves back and keeps it out.

OUT! TAKEN! Nathan Lyon gets rid of Ravichandran Ashwin as he tries to go big this time. Ripper! Ravichandran Ashwin flights this up, on middle, drifts and turns away sharply, Travis Head looks to sweep it away, but msises and it goes off his thigh pads and Srikar Bharat collects it. There is a huge appeal, but the finger stays down and Rohit Sharma decides against the review.
Looped up, full and on middle, Travis Head knocks it back to the bowler.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Marnus Labuschagne leans on and blocks it out.
Floated, full and on middle, Marnus Labuschagne keeps it out towards the bowler.
Flatter, full and on middle, Marnus Labuschagne defends it on the front foot.
Flighted, full and on middle, Marnus Labuschagne is solid in his defense again.
Short and on off, Marnus Labuschagne moves back and negotiates it well to the off side.
Quicker, full and on off, Marnus Labuschagne plays it towards silly point. A maiden over!
Short and around leg, Travis Head moves back and flicks it towards fine leg for a single.
Tossed up, full and on off, Marnus Labuschagne guides it towards point.

Floated, shortish and outside off, Marnus Labuschagne reaches for it block, but misses and it goes past the outside edge towards the keeper where Srikar Bharat collects it and disturb the stumps. There is an appeal for the stumping and the umpire goes upstairs. UltraEdge shows no bat involved and the replays shows that the back foot of Marnus Labuschagne is gorunded.
Slower through the air, on middle, Marnus Labuschagne stays there and blocks it out.
Short and on off, Marnus Labuschagne keeps it out onto the pitch.
FOUR! Easy runs! This is way short and outside off, Marnus Labuschagne moves back and punches it nicely through extra covers for a boundary.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Travis Head blocks it down the pitch.
Floated, short and on middle, Travis Head nudges it towards short mid-wicket.
Short again and outside off, Travis Head moves back and punches it through cover-point for a couple of runs.
Quicker, full and on middle, Travis Head drills it towards mid on.
Slightly shorter and around off, turning in, Travis Head dabs it towads cover-point.

FOUR! FIFTY FOR HEAD! This has come at a good time for Australia when they needed it. Axar Patel lands this short and outside off, Travis Head waits for it and late cuts it towards the vacant third man fence for a boundary.
Tossed up, full and on off, Marnus Labuschagne keeps it out to the off side.
Flatter, full and on off, Marnus Labuschagne opens the face of his bat and steers it wide of point for a single.
Flighted, full and on off, Travis Head tries to drive it away, but gets an inside edge onot his pads as the ball goes nowhere.
Short and on off, Travis Head moves back and pushes it towards short covers.
Looped up, full and on off, Travis Head drives it towards shrot covers.
Short and outside offf, Travis Head cuts it straight to point.
FOUR! Easy pickings! This is flatter, full and on the pads, Marnus Labuschagne tickles it towards the fine leg fence for a boundary. Australia lead by 2 runs now!
Floated, full and on middle, Marnus Labuschagne turns it to the leg side.
Tossed up, full and on off, Marnus Labuschagne leans on and blocks it out.
Quicker, short and on middle, Marnus Labuschagne keeps it out down the pitch.
Flatter, full and on off, Marnus Labuschagne steers it towards point.
Slower through the air, on off, turning away, Marnus Labuschagne prods forward to defend, but gets beaten by spin.
Quicker, full and on off, angling in, Travis Head stays back and keeps it out to the off side.
FOUR! Good shot! This is floated, full and on leg, Travis Head skips down the track and heaves it towards the deep mid-wicket fence for a boundary.
Short and outside off, Travis Head moves back and punches it towards sweeper covers for a single.
Short and on middle, Marnus Labuschagne moves back and nudges it through square leg for a run.
SIX! BANG! This is flighted, full and on middle, Travis Head stays there and dispatches it over the long on fence for a biggie.
Short and outside off, Travis Head cuts it towards covers where the fielder dives to his left to stop it.
Floated, full and on middle, Marnus Labuschagne defends it on the front foot.
Tossed up, full and on off, Marnus Labuschagne drives it through covers for a single.
Flatter, short and outside off, Travis Head leaves it alone.
FOUR! Travis Head is making his intent clear! This is flighted, full and on off, Travis Head uses his feet and smashes it wide of mid on for a boundary.
Short and outside off, Travis Head cuts it towards deep point for a single.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Marnus Labuschagne knocks it down the pitch.
Short and on off, Travis Head moves back and blocks it out.
Flatter, short and on middle, Travis Head pushes it back to the bowler.
Tossed up, full and on off, Travis Head eases it towards long on for a single.
Short and on off, Marnus Labuschagne guides it towards point.
Floated, full and on middle, Marnus Labuschagne keeps it out to the leg side.
Flighted, full and on middle, Marnus Labuschagne is solid in his defense again.

TWO BYES! Mohammad Shami starts a new spell from around the wicket and angles it well down the leg side, past the diving keeper as well. The ball rolls toward fine leg as the batters pick up a couple of byes.
Back of a length around middle, pushed away in front of mid-wicket for a couple of runs.
Pitched up on middle and leg, nudged away to short mid-wicket.
Full and reversing a bit onto the pads, Marnus Labuschagne flicks it down to fine leg for one.
FOUR! A bit too wide! Shorter and outside off, staying low, Travis Head reaches out and taps it wide of the fielder at deep backward point for a boundary.
Goes full and straight now, Head jams it out to mid on.
Floated up on off stump, Labuschagne keeps it down toward silly point.
A tad shorter around middle, blocked out.
A bit more round-arm and angling onto middle and leg, Labuschagne defends it with soft hands.
Comes from over the wicket now and floats it around leg stump, Labuschagne pads it away.
And again! Around leg stump, padded away wide of the man at short leg.
No ball! Flatter delivery on off stump, Labuschagne blocks it out. Ravindra Jadeja has overstepped and a no ball is called.
Flatter delivery on off stump, Labuschagne blocks it out.

Half an appeal for lbw but turned down. Fullish length, angling in a long way from middle and leg. Travis Head looks to flick but misses and the ball goes off the pads behind point. They pick up a leg bye.
Full and on off stump, reversing in sharply, Labuschagne keeps it out.
Length ball on the fourth stump line, Labuschagne defends from his crease.
Length again, reversing back into middle and off, Marnus Labuschagne blocks it off the front foot.
Very full on middle, ends up being a low full toss, Labuschagne pushes it back to the bowler.
On a good length over middle and leg, Labuschagne blocks it back on the deck.
Shorter one around off, played off the back foot toward cover.
Flatter and around off, staying a shade low, Travis Head leaves it alone.
Floated up outside off, inviting the drive and Head does drive but straight to extra cover.
Tossed up around middle, this is driven down to long on for a single.
Floated a bit fuller and around leg, Labuschagne puts out a big stride and pads it out.
Full again on leg stump, Labuschagne blocks it out.
Good length, angled into middle, Travis Head solidly keeps it out.
Full and straight now, Head drives it right back at the bowler who makes a good half-stop on the followthrough.
Bowls it back of a length around off and angling it in. Travis Head looks to hang back and pull but misses.
Ouch, that must have stung! Full and straight, Travis Head nails the straight drive right back at the bowler and Mohammad Shami gets a blow to the right boot.
Comes from over the wicket now and serves it on the pads, Travis Head flicks it through mid-wicket for a single.
A touch fuller on the pads, Labuschagne leans on and nudges it leg side.
Bowls it shorter, turning it in from around off, Head pushes it off the back foot in front of short leg.
Nicely bowled! Flighted delivery outside off, Travis Head looks for the expansive drive and gets an inside edge onto the pads.
Floated up full around off, Head drives it straight to mid off.
Flighted again around off, Travis Head strides out and looks to flick but misses and the ball goes off the pads. Just a stifled appeal for lbw but it is turned down.
Shorter and on off, flicked away off the back foot to mid-wicket.
Maiden! Fuller this time around off, pushed away to silly mid on.
A length ball on the fifth stump line, Labuschagne leaves it alone and the ball dies on its way to the keeper.
Pitches it a bit further up around off, Labuschagne blocks it out.
Good length outside off, tapped away wide of the point fielder for a single.
FOUR! Hammered away! A half-volley outside off, Travis Head stands tall and slaps it through the cover region for a boundary.
Fullish length outside off, caressed away through cover-point for a single.
Full and around middle, reversing in a bit, Labuschagne punches it toward mid on.
Flighted one around off, Head pushes it off the front back to the bowler.
Floated up around off, pushed away to extra cover.
Holds it back a touch and bowls it outside off, turning it in. Travis Head gets a big stride across and pushes it off the inside edge toward cover for a single.
Quicker and fuller around off, Marnus Labuschagne edges it down with soft hands past the slip cordon for a single.
Short and outside off, eased off the back foot in front of square on the off side for a couple of runs.
Floated up on a nagging length outside off, Travis Head strides out and looks to block but gets it off the pads toward cover. There is a stifled appeal for lbw once again and nothing more.
Full on middle and leg, clipped away in front of square leg for a single.
Length ball angling across the off stump, Travis Head eases it through the point region for a run.
On a good length around off, Labuschagne looks to drop and run but is sent back by Travis Head.
FOUR! Lovely timing on that one. Full again on the pads, Marnus Labuschagne flicks it gently but the ball races away through mid-wicket for a boundary.
Back of a length outside off, this is eased away to the right of the man at cover-point.
Fullish length, reversing in from around off, Labuschagne presents a dead bat at it.
Gives it some flight and bowls it around the legs, Head nudges it out on the leg side.
A tad shorter on middle, Travis Head blocks it out.
Floated down leg, Head comes forward and flicks it toward backward square leg for a single.
This is tossed up on the pads, Labuschagne clips it away toward mid-wicket and rotates the strike.
Holds it back a touch and bowls it shorter around leg. Travis Head looks to come forward but the ball hits a rough and takes off, Head adjusts well to go on the back foot and keep it out.
TWO BYES! Floated up down the leg side, Travis Head looks to flick but misses and the ball eludes the keeper as well. The batters pick up a couple of byes.
FOUR! A bit too full and on the legs, Marnus Labuschagne nicely tucks it away through square leg for an easy boundary. Labuschagne moves to 49 now.

Shorter one on the hips, Marnus Labuschagne works it away 'round the corner for a couple of runs. That will be FIFTY for Labuschagne, his first of the tour and it has come on the final day of the Test series as well, solid knock from him.
This is pitched up on off and middle, Labuschagne blocks it to mid on.
Back of a length around off, Labuschagne gets behind the line of the ball and keeps it out.
Good length on off stump, Labuschagne stays solid in defense.
Hard length around off, kept down on the off side.

Positive running from the batters and Ashwin is not happy with a bit of sluggish fielding from Ravindra Jadeja in the deep. Shorter and on the pads, Travis Head tucks it away in front of mid-wicket and Jadeja just waits for the ball to come to him. The batters sense the opportunity and push for the second, Jadeja picks up the pace but they make it with ease.
Shorter again down leg, keeping a bit low, this is flicked away past square leg for a single.
Around middle, blocked out.
NTossed up on off and middle, Labuschagne defends it off the front foot.
Slower and shorter on middle, Labuschagne blocks it from inside his crease.
Nicely bowled! Ravichandran Ashwin sees Marnus Labuschagne coming down the track and shortens the length, giving it more air as well. Labuschagne adjusts and pushes it back to the bowler.

OUT! TIMBER! A ripper of a delivery from Axar Patel and what a way to get to his 50th Test wicket. Axar comes from over the wicket and starts off with a floater outside off stump. Travis Head gets drawn into the drive and ends up playing away from the body. Head doesn't reach the pitch of the delivery and the ball turns in sharply to beat the inside edge and knock over the top of off stump. Head cannot believe it and he has to depart for a well-made 90.
Comes from around the wicket and angles in a flatter delivery into leg stump. Steven Smith goes on the back foot to keep it out.
Quicker one around off, Steven Smith gets forward to block.
Quicker and flatter, attacking the off stump, Smith rocks back to defend.
Angling into middle, Smith keeps it out.
A wicket-maiden! Floated up around off and middle, Steven Smith pushes it off the front foot in front of silly point.
Floated, short and on off, turning in, Marnus Labuschagne moves back and turns it past short leg.
Tossed up, full and on off, Marnus Labuschagne leans on and blocks it out.
Short and on middle, Marnus Labuschagne nudges it towards square leg.
Flatter, full and on off, Marnus Labuschagne squeezes it towards point.
Flighted, full and on off, Marnus Labuschagne keeps it out to the off side.
Looped up, full and on off, Marnus Labuschagne defends it on the front foor. Two maidens in a row!
Tossed up, full and on middle, Steven Smith blocks it back to the bowler.
Floated, short and on middle, Steven Smith knocks it to the right of the bowler.
Flighted and around middle, Steven Smith uses is feet and tries to defend, but it hits his pad first. There is a stiffled appeal for LBW, but turned down.
Flatter, short and on off, turning away, Steven Smith steers it towards point.
Quicker, full and on off, Steven Smith keeps it out to the off side.

DROPPED! Steven Smith gets a life here! Axar Patel slows it up, on off, turning away sharply, Steven Smith prods forward to defend, but gets an outside edge towards the keeper where Srikar Bharat fails to cover the line and the ball hits him on the pads.
Floated, full and on middle, Marnus Labuschagne blocks it out.
Tossed up, full and on off, Marnus Labuschagne defends it on the front foot.
FOUR! Lovely shot! Ravichandran Ashwin lands this short and outside off, Marnus Labuschagne rocks back and punches it through covers for a boundary.
Flighted, full and on off, Marnus Labuschagne squeezes it towards point for a single.
Floated and on off, Steven Smith uses his feet and knocks it down the pitch.
Short and on middle, Steven Smith tucks it towards short mid-wicket.
Flatter, full and on leg, Marnus Labuschagne turns it towards short mid-wicket.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Marnus Labuschagne leans on and blocks it down the pitch.
Quicker, short and on middle, Marnus Labuschagne pushes it towards short covers.
Angles this one into the batter, on middle, Marnus Labuschagne keeps it out to the leg side.
Slower through the air, on middle, Marnus Labuschagne watches it through and negotiates it well.
Flatter, full and on off, turns away a bit, Marnus Labuschagne prods forward to defend, but gets beaten on the outside edge. THAT WILL BE TEA ON DAY 5!
Tossed up, full and on middle, Steven Smith blocks it out.
FOUR! Nice shot! This is floated and around middle, Steven Smith skips down the track and lofts it over mid on for a boundary.
Bowls this a fraction short and outside off. Steven Smith blocks this into the off side.
Floats this one full and outside off. Steven Smith blocks this back to the bowler.
Short once again and into the pads. Steven Smith goes deep in the crease and keeps it out.
Tosses this one full and in line with the stumps. Steven Smith dabs this back down the pitch.
Axar Patel floats this full and on a leg stump line. Marnus Labuschagne defends this to the right of the bowler.
Tosses this one full and outside off. Marnus Labuschagne defends this one solidly.
Bowls this closer to the off pole on a fuller length. Marnus Labuschagne taps this towards cover.
Goes full once again and into the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne blocks this back to the bowler.
Fires this one full and at the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne continues to defend solidly.
Strays onto the pads on a shortish length. Marnus Labuschagne dabs this into the leg side.
Tossed up, full and on off, Steven Smith blocks it out.
Floated, full and on off, Steven Smith defends it on the front foot.
FOUR! Cut away! Ravindra Jadeja lands this short and outside off, Steven Smith waits for it and cuts it away through point for a boundary.
Flighted, full and on middle, Steven Smith knocks it down the pitch.
Gives this one some air as well, on off, Steven Smith keeps it out to the off side.
Flatter, full and on middle, Steven Smith pushes it to the right of the bowler.
Axar Patel floats this full and in line with the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne blocks it back down the pitch.
Strays onto the pads on a shorter length. Marnus Labuschagne dabs this towards square leg.
Tosses-up delivery bowled full and outside off. Marnus Labuschagne taps this towards point.
Goes full again and into the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne smothers this into the pitch.
Flighted delivery bowled full and outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne pushes at this and gets an outside edge towards third man for a couple of runs.
Bowls this at the stumps on a fuller length. Marnus Labuschagne flicks this towards mid-wicket.
Ravindra Jadeja floats this one full and just outside off. Steven Smith defends this towards short cover.
Skids through with the arm into the stumps. Steven Smith goes back and keeps this one out.
Loops this one full and outside off. Steven Smith knocks this to short cover.
Continues to bowl full and at the stumps. Steven Smith blocks this back to the bowler.
Short this time and outside the off stump. Steven Smith cuts this straight to point.
Flights this one full and outside the off pole. Steven Smith opts to leave this one alone.
Axar Patel tosses this one full and way outside the off pole. Marnus Labuschagne does not offer a shot.
Floats this one full and outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne continues to shoulder arms to it.
This is slightly short and outside off. Marnus Labuschagne goes back in the crease and cuts this to deep cover-point for a run.
Loops this one full and outside off. Steven Smith drives this hard to short cover.
Gets this one to go with the arm into the stumps on a shorter length. Steven Smith pushes this towards mid-wicket.
Bowls this one a touch fuller and outside the off stump. Steven Smith punches this to the fielder at short cover.
Ravindra Jadeja tosses this one a tad bit short and outside off. Marnus Labuschagne slaps this towards deep cover-point and picks up a brace.
Floats this one full and outside off. Marnus Labuschagne pushes this towards point.
Flights this full and wide outside off, gets some turn. Marnus Labuschagne raises his arms and leaves it alone.
Slightly short this time and outside the off pole. Marnus Labuschagne knocks this towards point.
Fires this one full and wide outside off. Marnus Labuschagne is not tempted to play at it.
Loopy delivery this time bowled full and just outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne gets forward and blocks this to the left of the bowler.
Axar Patel fires this one full and into the stumps. The ball stays a fraction low but Steven Smith gets his bat down in time and keeps the ball out.
Floats this one full and at the stumps. Steven Smith clips this towards mid-wicket.
Tosses this one full and in line with the stumps. Steven Smith defends this back to the bowler.
Angles this into the pads on a fuller length. Steven Smith dabs this towards mid-wicket.
Continues to attack the pads on a fuller length. Steven Smith blocks this towards mid on.
Bowls this one short and into the legs. Steven Smith tucks this towards deep square leg and picks up a couple of runs.
Ravindra Jadeja floats this one full and in line with the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne defends this back down the pitch.
Full delivery on middle. Marnus Labuschagne blocks this one out.
Tosses this one full and just outside off. Marnus Labuschagne dabs this back towards the bowler.
Loopy delivery bowled full and outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne leaves this one alone.
Continues to bowl just outside off on a fuller length. Marnus Labuschagne happy to block this one out.
Floats this one into the stumps on a fuller length. Marnus Labuschagne knocks this back to the bowler.
Axar Patel floats this one full and into the stumps. Steven Smith defends this back to the bowler.
Full and outside the off stump. Steven Smith leaves this one alone.
Flighted, full and on middle, Steven Smith defends it on the front foot.
BEATEN! Axar Patel bowls this quicker with angle, on middle, turns away sharply, Steven Smith leans on a defend, but gets beaten on the outside edge.
Flatter, full and on middle, Steven Smith turns it to the leg side.
Looped up, full and on middle, Steven Smith knocks it down the pitch.
Ravindra Jadeja floats this one full and into the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne dabs this towards square leg.
Really full this time and at the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne keeps this out into the off side.
Tosses this full and straight. Marnus Labuschagne blocks this back down the pitch.
Wider outside off on a fuller length. Marnus Labuschagne keeps this out on the off side.
Loops this one full and outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne knocks this towards short cover.
Goes straight once again and really full. Marnus Labuschagne defends this one solidly.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Steven Smith leans on and blocks it out.
Floated, full and on off, Steven Smith stays back and keeps it out to the off side.
Slower through the air, on off with extra bounce, Steven Smith proids forward and defends it out wiht the top half of the bat.
Flighted, full and on middle, Steven Smith turns it to the leg side.
Looped up, full and on middle, Steven Smith is solid in his defense again.
Flatter, full and on middle, Steven Smith knocks it down the pitch.
Shubman Gill floats this one full and outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne defends this back down pitch.
Bowls this slightly short and spinning in from outside off. Marnus Labuschagne dabs this into the leg side.
Tosses this one full and in line with the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne smothers this into the pitch.
Short once again and at the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne clips this to deep backward square leg and takes a single.
Loops this one full and just outside off. Steven Smith knocks this back to the bowler.
Goes back to bowling short and just outside off. Steven Smith rocks back and defends this back down the pitch.
Cheteshwar Pujara tosses this one on a shortish length and outside off. Marnus Labuschagne punches this to deep cover for a single.
Floats this one full and just outside off. Steven Smith knocks this back to the bowler.
Bowls this on a shortish length and just outside off. Steven Smith pushes this towards cover on the back foot.
A loopy delivery bowled full and at the stumps. Steven Smith drives this towards mid off.
Another flighted delivery bowled full and in line with the stumps. Steven Smith works this towards cover.
Bowls this short and angles this into the stumps. It stays slightly low but Steven Smith manages to keep this one out.
Shubman Gill floats this one full and just outside off. Marnus Labuschagne blocks this towards mid on.
